(189010,'Finance Club NYC Immersion Trip',cast('2012-11-08 10:30' as date),cast('2012-11-10 14:30' as date),'New York City',NULL,NULL,'HTC','On this trip, students will have the chance to interact and network with alumni and other professionals in the financial world - in both corporate and social settings. Students will arrive in New York City Thursday Evening, and will rest before visiting alumni and other professionals within several New York Based financial service firms and banks on Friday. Afterwards, students will have the opportunity to meet, socialize, and network with Hudson Alumni working in the financial industry at a dinner. Students will return Saturday Morning. ',200),
