(196143,'Thanksgiving Brown Bag',cast('2012-11-15 11:30' as date),cast('2012-11-15 13:00' as date),'Alana Multipurpose Room',NULL,NULL,'NAIS','Professor Kerber and students from the Native American Student Association will lead a brown bag lunch and discussion on the Thanksgiving myth and misconceptions regarding the celebration of this holiday.'||chr(10)||' ',280),
