(220017,'CAB Take Two: Hello, I Must Be Going',cast('2013-01-25 22:00' as date),cast('2013-01-25 23:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,NULL,'SAA','CAB take two presents Hello, I must Be Going:'||chr(10)||'Circumstances force a young divorcee to move back in with her parents in suburban Connecticut, where an affair with a younger guy rejuvenates her passion for life.'||chr(10)||'from imdb.com',null),
(220060,'Hudson Activities Fair',cast('2013-01-24 16:30' as date),cast('2013-01-24 18:30' as date),'The HOP/Clark Room (in James C. Hudson Hall)',NULL,NULL,'SGA','Any and every activity you could be a part of will be there! Get out there and get involved, the best experiences you will have in college will be in following your passions or trying new things outside the classroom. Meet people, do something special and sign yourself up!',360),
(225877,'Poetry Open Mic Night Featuring: Jose Canta',cast('2013-03-29 20:00' as date),cast('2013-03-29 20:30' as date),'Donovan''s Pub',NULL,NULL,'DPS','A poetry open mic night emceed by and featuring Jose Canta, professional poet and Hamilton College graduate.  The show will emphasize the experiences of this first-generation Latino as well as feature the unique creations of our own student body. ',500),
(229605,'ATMA Regional Tournament',cast('2013-02-22 14:00' as date),cast('2013-02-24 22:00' as date),'Buffalo, NY',NULL,NULL,'MT','The mock trial team will be participating in the American Mock Trial Association''s Regional Tournament in Buffalo, NY this February. This is the first of a series of three tournaments sponsored by the American Mock Trial Association, culiminating with the National Championships in April. ',310),
