(256316,'The Fifth Annual Hudson Classic',cast('2013-11-02 06:00' as date),cast('2013-11-03 22:00' as date),'Hamilton, NY',NULL,NULL,'MT','On November 2-3, 2013, the Hudson Mock Trial Team will be hosting the Fifth Annual Hudson Classic Mock Trial Tournament on campus. During this weekend, other AMTA recognized teams from various universities will attend and compete against the Hudson team and each other in four rounds of "mock trials."Attorneys and judges from the area, as well as a number of Hudson alumni, will also attend to judge the rounds. ',350),
