(256344,'Bienvenidos BBQ',cast('2013-08-29 12:30' as date),cast('2013-08-29 13:30' as date),'La Casa',NULL,NULL,'LASO','The Bienvenidos BBQ is an event for all incoming Latino/Hispanic students to meet other Latino/Hispanic students, and anyone other Hudson students that are interested in coming to the BBQ. This is a networking/social event with catered food and Latino music to demonstrate some of Hudsons diversity. ',190),
(270378,'Welcome Back Release Night',cast('2013-09-06 18:30' as date),cast('2013-09-06 19:30' as date),'ALANA Lounge',NULL,NULL,'BSU','Release Night is an opportunity for students on campus to express themselves and speak on social, political, and economic concerns that they have been pondering. It is a welcoming and encouraging space for dialogue to occur on the basis of the type of concerns, questions, and aspirations that Hudson students raise to one another. The Black Student Union takes great pride in celebrating students voices. Through the hosting of Release Nights we provide this platform.'||chr(10)||'Essentially, it is a chance to gain support and recognition through others about the struggles and achievements that Hudson students may be enduring. Students are provided a support structure, which allows them to openly voice their thoughts without fear of being judged. We want to especially hold a Welcome Back Release Night event to attract first-years so they feel comfortable actively interacting with students on their own terms, with regard to what it is they feel they want to share.',375),
(281691,'Take Two Saturday Matinee: Silver Linings Playbook',cast('2013-04-27 15:30' as date),cast('2013-04-27 16:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,NULL,'SAA','CAB Take Two present:'||chr(10)||'Silver Linings Playbook (Fri 7pm, Sat 3:30pm and 10pm) '||chr(10)||'After a stint in a mental institution, former teacher Pat Solitano moves back in with his parents and tries to reconcile with his ex-wife. Things get more challenging when Pat meets Tiffany, a mysterious girl with problems of her own.'||chr(10)||'The Hobbit: An Expected Journey (Fri 10pm, Sat 7pm) '||chr(10)||'A younger and more reluctant Hobbit, Bilbo Baggins, sets out on an "unexpected journey" to the Lonely Mountain with a spirited group of Dwarves to reclaim their stolen mountain home from a dragon named Smaug.'||chr(10)||' ',400),
(281747,'Student Involvement Fair',cast('2013-09-03 16:00' as date),cast('2013-09-03 17:00' as date),'Academic Quad (HOP and Huntington if rain)',NULL,NULL,'SGA','If you are interested in joining a student organization at Hudson, come to the student involvement fair! Representatives from each student organization will be available to tell you more about their organizations and recruit new members. ',200),
