(7421359,'Yoga Fundraiser Supporting the West Penn Oncology T7 Wing in Honor of Sarah Finton',cast('2021-09-23 17:00' as date),cast('2021-09-23 17:00' as date),'Online','Fundraising','Philanthropy','KKG','Sarah Finton was recently diagnosed with a specific type of Leukemia called Acute Promyelocytic Leukemia (APL). Sarah was admitted to the hospital and will remain at West Penn Hospital in Pittsburgh for one month for in-patient treatment, followed by outpatient treatment near home. She has withdrawn from Hudson for the semester but is planning to be back in January so she can continue volunteering at SOMAC and crushing her classes! '||chr(10)||'Come to support Sarah through this virtual yoga fundraiser in which money raised will be donated to her wing at the hospital to help fund further research and equipment for Acute Promyelocytic Leukemia. '||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||' ',230),
