(7851482,'Sex Museum. Welcome to the "Village" of Hot Spots: The Paths to Orgasm and Pleasure',cast('2022-03-08 17:30' as date),cast('2022-03-08 19:30' as date),'COOP','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'ALANA','The Sex Education series continues. '||chr(10)||'This time we invite you to the "Village of Hot Spots" to celebrate the International Women''s Day.'||chr(10)||'You will have a chance to explore the Sex Toys Corner, have a ride through the Orgasm Boulevard, pick some valuable tips on the Sexual Health Lane, play game at the Fun "Anatomy" Terrace. Do not forget to turn to the Queer* Alley and visit the Square of the Broken Glass where you can learn how to manage your anger.'||chr(10)||'And many more interesting adventures! '||chr(10)||'P.S. Open your mind, embrace your sexuality, and learn how to experience pleasure and being able to communicate pleasure to your partner (partners), sexual partners etc.',null),
