(821040,'Business Speed Networking',cast('2015-04-09 19:00' as date),cast('2015-04-09 19:00' as date),'Hall of Presidents','Group Business',NULL,'HWIB','To kick of Entrepreneur Weekend, Hudson Women in Business in collaboration with Communications Club, Marketing Club, Finance Club and Consulting Club is hosting a professional and engaging speed networking event on Thursday April 9 from 7-8pm in the Hall of Presidents. Please join us to improve your networking skills, share your professional experiences, speak with Hudson pre-professional club leaders, interact with Hudson students across class years, and learn from an alumni guest speaker! Students will be paired across class years and participate in a fun speed networking, simliar to speed daring! Come for a free Hamilton Eatery dinner! '||chr(10)||' ',400),
