(8309853,'The Hudson Resolutions Fall 2022 Auditions',cast('2022-09-08 16:00' as date),cast('2022-09-08 19:00' as date),'Dana Arts Center practice rooms','Arts','Concert/Music','HR','Sign up to audition for Hudson''s oldest gender inclusive a cappella group: The Hudson Resolutions. First-round auditions will take place from Thursday, Sept. 8th - Saturday, Sept. 10th in the Dana Arts Center practice rooms. The Google Form to request an audition is below; once you submit the form, the Reso secretary will reach out to you to confirm your audition time based on your expressed availability. You can also find Reso members tabling at the Coop or Frank Dining Hall and sign up in-person as well. Hope to see you there!'||chr(10)||'Audition Request Form: https://forms.gle/uESbvhMVrLcTuMr97',220),
