(857318,'Hudson Women in Business Spring 2016 Immersion Trip',cast('2016-03-03 16:00' as date),cast('2016-03-05 10:00' as date),'Crowne Plaza Times Square NYC','Group Business',NULL,'HWIB','This is a two-day trip to New York City to allow our members to make valuable connections with alumnae and gain insights into the opportunities that lie ahead post-graduation.',null),
(8657399,'Rummikub Championship',cast('2023-01-05 14:00' as date),cast('2023-01-05 18:00' as date),'Multipurpose Room','Social',NULL,'ALANA','Join us in a board game competition focusing on strategic moves involving number tiles. Instructions and guidance will be provided before each game. No experience is needed. All are welcome and dinner is provided!'||chr(10)||'The competition will be held from 2pm-5pm and dinner will start at 5pm. '||chr(10)||'For more information, you can go to this link or go to the University events calendar. '||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'Please note some events require registration in advance as space is limited. For any trips, each student must complete an Acknowledgment of Risk and Responsibility form and bring it with them to the bus when they are traveling. Any approved guests must do the same. Students are welcome to wear masks while riding on shuttles or in vans. ',null),
(8717361,'Cupid''s Fever: Sex Toys Bingo',cast('2023-02-14 18:00' as date),cast('2023-02-14 20:00' as date),'Center for Women''s Studies','Social',NULL,'ALANA','Looking forward to celebrating Valentine''s Day and having fun?'||chr(10)||'Join our Cupid''s Fever Night! '||chr(10)||'We are going to have an amazing celebration by playing Sex Toys Bingo (prizes are guaranteed), getting engaged in fun games, receiving vital tips and participating in myths busting surrounded sexuality and sex. '||chr(10)||'We will provide you with aphrodisiacs (aka food, pastries, and sweets).'||chr(10)||'Do not hesitate! Come and bring your friends! '||chr(10)||' ',null),
(8912565,'Sex Museum , Holy Moly: Sexuality and Spirituality',cast('2023-03-08 17:00' as date),cast('2023-03-08 19:00' as date),'TV Room','Spirituality',NULL,'ALANA','On March 8, another Sex Museum opens its doors.'||chr(10)||'We invite you to explore the spiritual corners of sexuality intersected with a long tradition of pleasure.'||chr(10)||'Learn more about intimacy through dance; relaxation through taking care of your body and soul; and sexuality representations throughout the history.'||chr(10)||'Various activities and fun!'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'P.S. Q-Center (ACR Health) is offering a free STI/STD testing.',null),
(909331,'The Thickness with Rupi Kaur',cast('2016-02-25 18:00' as date),cast('2016-02-25 19:00' as date),'Creative Arts House (100 Broad St)','Arts',NULL,'SRT','Rupi Kaur is an artist, storyteller, poet and photographer from Toronto, Canada whose work tackles issues of love, healing and trauma. Ms. Kaur is the writer of a must read poetry collection, Milk and Honey. Ms. Kaurs raw engagement with prose, metaphors, and challenging topics of everyday life as a woman of color allows her work to resonate with and serve as a source of inspiration and motivation for her readers and audiences, and makes her the perfect guest for an event that aims to get into the thickness of our various identities. This event will allow the Hudson community to learn about or at least get an idea on how to tackles issues of love, healing, hurting and trauma through Ms. Kaurs work and to explore the multitudes of thickness in their identities. Also to explore their intersectionality and reflect about themselves in the gaze of poetry.',null),
(909338,'Meditation session',cast('2016-02-09 12:15' as date),cast('2016-02-09 13:00' as date),'Judd Chapel','Spirituality',NULL,'HBC','Biweekly meditations at the Judd Chapel in Chapel basement. Meditations will be combined with Buddhist teachings in the hope of helping all to gain more understanding and practice of compassion and wisdom. No previous experience needed. All are welcome.',null),
