(292937,'French Club Coffee Hour',cast('2013-09-25 16:00' as date),cast('2013-09-25 16:00' as date),'French Seminar Room, Lawrence 205',NULL,NULL,'FC','Come practice your French speaking skills with other students and learn about different aspects of French culture while enjoying coffee, tea, and pastries!',null),
