(239000,'"Waste Land" as part of SEA''s Environmental Film Series',cast('2013-03-21 19:00' as date),cast('2013-03-21 20:00' as date),'Ho 101',NULL,'Movie/Film','SEA','Weekly 4-part film series that focuses on environmental issues including energy, waste, water, and marine life.  Food will be included and discussions after the movies will be either formally (guest speaker) or informally (slide with questions) facilitated.  The tentative dates are March 7th, March 21st, April 4th, and April 11th at 7:00pm.',null),
(239561,'"Tapped" as part of SEA''s Environmental Film Series',cast('2013-04-11 19:00' as date),cast('2013-04-11 20:00' as date),'Coop Conference Room (behind fireplace)',NULL,'Movie/Film','SEA','Weekly 4-part film series that focuses on environmental issues including energy, waste, water, and marine life.  Food from the Hamilton Eatery will be included and there will be a short discussion after the movies.',null),
(239562,'"King Corn" as part of SEA''s Environmental Film Series',cast('2013-03-28 19:00' as date),cast('2013-03-28 20:00' as date),'Ho 101',NULL,'Movie/Film','SEA','Weekly 4-part film series that focuses on environmental issues including energy, waste, water, and marine life.  Food from the Hamilton Eatery will be included and there will be a short discussion after the movie.',null),
