(3230299,'POC Formal',cast('2019-02-28 21:00' as date),cast('2019-03-01 00:00' as date),'The Hourglass','Social',NULL,'BSU','In honor of Black History Month, the Black Student Union (BSU) and would like to host a formal at the Hourglass for the members of all recognized ALANA groups. This event will be a way to bring members of Hudsons multicultural groups together in a fun and memorable way. Attendees will have a chance to interact with new people, enjoy music from other cultures, and students who are 21+ will have the opportunity to purchase drinks throughout the night. As the second annual Black History Month formal, this event is highly anticipated due to its immense success last year and is hopefully on its way to becoming a BSU staple.',360),
