(4815327,'Dogs of Hudson',cast('2019-08-29 17:00' as date),cast('2019-08-29 17:00' as date),'Academic Quad','Social',NULL,'SAA','Its a parade of puppies! Meet and greet the furry faces of Hudson University. Pups will have their own profile so you can learn fun facts about them: favorite toys, snacks, and activities. Sponsored by the Hudson Activities Board',null),
