(4875667,'Preference Night',cast('2019-09-14 13:00' as date),cast('2019-09-14 18:00' as date),'Gamma Phi Beta House','Social',NULL,'GPB','Final night of recruitment in which members are paired with PNMS to deeply discuss their experiences in Gphi. Two speeches by Gphi members will be given at each party. ',300),
(4894181,'Theta Chi Backyard Cookout',cast('2019-09-13 18:00' as date),cast('2019-09-13 18:00' as date),'Theta Chi','Social',NULL,'TC','Our chef, Gerry Nash, will be cooking up his famous chicken and ribs in the backyard. This event gives individuals in the recruiting process another opporunity to meet the brothers of Theta Chi.',null),
