(5602470,'Gamma Phi Beta Spring Crush',cast('2020-02-13 21:00' as date),cast('2020-02-14 00:00' as date),'The Hourglass','Social',NULL,'GPB','Gamma Phi Beta''s annual fall crush event where every sister invites one date. It will take place downtown at the Hourglass. Food (wings, pizza, cheese and crackers, veggies and dip) and non-alcoholic beverages are available to everyone and a cash bar to those over 21. ',400),
