(5604064,'Saturday Afternoon Dry Party with Close Friends',cast('2020-02-15 15:00' as date),cast('2020-02-15 19:00' as date),'Beta Theta Pi','Social',NULL,'BTP','On Saturday, February 15th, the brothers of Beta Theta Pi plan to host a dry event in their dining room, main entry area, and living room. Attendees for the event will include the brothers of the house and their close friends on campus. We will provide a variety of non-alcoholic beverages and snacks in the spaces being used for the event. There will be no theme but our dining room setup will include normal speakers and because this event is during the day we plan on having fewer lighting fixtures and more natural light. We have one student planned to play music throughout the duration of the event as attendees can dance, play billiards, and catch up. Two student monitors will be placed at the door for the duration of the event and we will also provide light snacks for all guests. Attendance will not exceed 120. Andrew Chung and Nick Sharma will be the social hosts for the event.',150),
