(623107,'Inflatable Games on Quad',cast('2015-09-25 15:00' as date),cast('2015-09-25 16:00' as date),'Academic Quad','Social',NULL,'SAA','There will be six inflatable games on the Acadademic Quad (Adrenaline Rush Obstacle Course, Wrecking Ball, Rapid Fire, Human Bowling, Gladiator Jouse, Boulder Das). This will be a great event for everyone to have fun and come together on the Quad.',null),
(623112,'Newman Lunches',cast('2015-09-07 12:15' as date),cast('2015-09-07 12:15' as date),'Chapel Basement','Spirituality',NULL,'NC','You are invited to the Newman Community''s Newman lunches, held on mondays in the Chapel Garden Level from 12:15-1:10.  The lunch series includes speakers from the Hudson faculty, Hudson student body, and outside speakers, usually discussiong topics that center on the teachings of the Catholic Church.  Lunches are catered by local restuarants.',null),
