(7092802,'Spreading Awareness of Minorities Suffering on Campus',cast('2021-04-29 15:00' as date),cast('2021-04-29 16:00' as date),'ALANA Cultural Center','Social',NULL,'OASIS','Join us for a peaceful demonstration on Hudson''s campus to spread awareness about the suffering of minority groups on campus. Too long have we felt neglected in a time we need support the most. We hope this will provide an active way for students to relieve any stress they have, while letting our voices be heard across the campus. Several posters are available to hand out, but we encourage you to make and bring your own poster as to avoid contact with other objects. '||chr(10)||'We will meet at ALANA at 3. We will also be distributing the shirts that have been purchased through our fundraiser during this time. Weather permitting, we will then walk down to Broad Street and remain there for the rest of the time.'||chr(10)||'NOTE: In the event that it rains, the walk will be cancelled but ALANA Cultural Center will remain open for those who need a change of scenery or a safe space to talk about whatever''s on their mind. As finals are coming up, the stress only increases, so it''s important to frequently check in with ourselves and others. ',60),
(7219753,'Trip to NYS Fair',cast('2021-08-29 11:00' as date),cast('2021-08-29 22:45' as date),'New York State Fair','Social',NULL,'SAA','Explore the largest fair in all of New York State! Sign up to reserve your spot on the bus. Transportation is provided.',null),
