(749078,'OASIS Family Dinners',cast('2015-09-15 17:00' as date),cast('2015-09-15 17:00' as date),'Bunche House','Cultural',NULL,'OASIS','Family dinner is a biweekly bonding events that provide an opportunity for not only OASIS members, but also all Asian students on campus to enjoy a relexing but interesting conversation about Asian identities.  We will cook and eat home food together. It gives us the opportunities to really get together and know more about each other in a more casual setting compared to our weekly meeting, which talks mostly about issues and problems with regard to Asian identities.',null),
