(775294,'Home Brown Bag',cast('2015-10-21 17:30' as date),cast('2015-10-21 18:00' as date),'Curtis Hall','Social',NULL,'SGA','"Home is where the heart is?"Join SGA, Link Staff, Konosioni, and Residential Commons for an open discussion on the significance of ''home'', navigating Hudson as a home away from home, and ways to make it a more inclusive living space for all. This Wednesday, October 21st from 5:30 P.M. to 7:00 P.M. on Curtis 1st Floor. Oliveri''s/Slices will be served for dinner!Student Speakers will include:Hunter Hillman ''16 (Konosioni, SGA)Isabelle James ''16 (Konosioni, Link Staff, SGA)Chloe Tawaststjerna ''17 (Link Staff)Hyeon Jeong ''18 (Link Staff, SGA)JuliaPaige Joseph ''18 (Link Staff)',510),
(779006,'EPIDEMIOLOGY BROWN BAG: EFFECTS OF HELICOBACTER PYLORI INFECTION ON THE RISK OF CHILDHOOD ANEMIA: AN EPIDEMIOLOGICAL RESEARCH USING ETHIOPIAN BIRTH COHORT',cast('2015-10-29 12:00' as date),cast('2015-10-29 12:00' as date),'Lawrence 105','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'HGHC','Professor Bineyam Taye will present on his epidemiological research based in Ethiopia. Lunch will be served! ',400),
