(812665,'Harvard World Model United Nations, Princeton Interactive Crisis Simulation, Chicago Model United Nations Conference',cast('2016-02-18 12:00' as date),cast('2016-02-18 13:00' as date),'Rome, Italy; Princeton, NJ; Chicago, IL','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'MUN','Giving students the opportunity to debate international issues alongside universities domestically and internationally. We prepare our members through weekly meetings to perfect their public speaking, research, and writing skills! ',null),
(812673,'Konosioni Charity Auction 2016',cast('2016-04-08 20:00' as date),cast('2016-04-08 20:30' as date),'Hall of Presidents','Fundraising',NULL,'THS','The 19th Annual Konosioni Charity Auction.'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'All proceeds from the auction will benefit non-profit organizations in Upstate NY through Madison County Gives. Last year''s event raised more than $24,000 that was distributed to seven local organizations. We look forward to once again making an impact within the broader community that Hudson calls home, thanks in part to your support. '||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'Past and current auction items include plane tickets, homemade goods, vacation stays in Colorado, Panama, and St. Lucia, Yankees or Red Sox tickets, babysitting services, tickets to the Tonight Show, language lessons and more. If you have an item or opportunity you can to contribute to the auction-- big or small-- please contact Sofia Estay ''16 (sestay@hudson.edu) at your earliest convenience. We hope you can make it to one of the largest student-run philanthropic events on campus.',290),
(816889,'Raider Roar',cast('2015-12-16 21:00' as date),cast('2015-12-16 22:00' as date),'5th Floor Case Library Patio','Social',NULL,'SGA','Come get out all of that pent up stress at the SGAs biannual Raider Roar study break at 9PM on Wednesday, December 16th at the fifth floor entrance of Case. Join students, administrators, faculty, and, of course, the Raider for free slices, warm beverages, and de-stressing. Dean Suzy Nelson and President-Elect Brian Casey will count-down from 13 to an epic roar that will shake Case Library to its very foundation. Dont miss this event!',300),
(8347962,'International Student Welcome/Welcome Back Dinner',cast('2022-09-16 17:15' as date),cast('2022-09-16 20:00' as date),'ALANA Cultural Center','Cultural',NULL,'HIC','WELCOME AND WELCOME BACK!!! CIC is holding a welcoming dinner at ALANA. Come and have a taste of authentic Chinese and Middle East food!!! Local students are also welcome to celebrate together with the international student body to enjoy the multicultural atmosphere. After having dinner, there will be various activities for students to socialize: board games, cultural trivia, karaoke, photo booth, and more!!! '||chr(10)||'p.s. (1) Please bring your own drink (2) the dinner is first come, first served.'||chr(10)||'Also, when not having dinner, feel free the wear a mask if you feel uncomfortable during the gathering! :)',200),
(848299,'Donovan''s Pub Trivia',cast('2016-01-21 19:30' as date),cast('2016-01-21 21:30' as date),'Donovan''s Pub','Social',NULL,'SAA','Grab your friends and head to Donovan''s Pub for Trivia Night every Thursday! Teams will compete for SUN Cash prizes, winning up to $75 for a first-place victory! Donovan''s Pub accepts the meal plan, cash, credit/debit, and SUN Cash for payment, so swing by the kitchen for some snacks or a drink, then grab a table for some trivia',null),
