(940339,'MCG Brown Bag: What is Service in Madison County?',cast('2016-04-07 11:30' as date),cast('2016-04-07 12:00' as date),'Lathrop 207','Community Service',NULL,'THS','An open discussion about service in Madison County and how students are (and aren''t) involved.'||chr(10)||'Members of local non-profit organizations participating are Community Bikes, Friends of Rogers, Food Bank of CNY, Hamilton Food Cupboard, Fiver Children''s Foundation, Mohawk Valley Resource Center for Refugees, and Community Action Partnership.'||chr(10)||'LUNCH PROVIDED by Curtain Call! ',400),
