(9560395,'Friday Night Party With Friends',cast('2023-10-27 22:00' as date),cast('2023-10-28 01:00' as date),'88 Broad St','Social',NULL,'BTP',NULL||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'Resubmission with Changed Sober Monitors'||chr(10)||'Friday, October 27th, the brothers of Beta Theta Pi plan to host a dry event in their library, main entry area, living room and dining room. Attendees will include the brothers of the house and close friends on campus. We will provide a variety of non-alcoholic beverages and snacks in the spaces being used for the event. There is no theme yet for this party, and our dining room setup will include speakers and lighting fixtures. We have one student planned to play music throughout the duration of the event, and attendees will be able to dance and catch up. Two student monitors will be at the door for the duration of the event, in addition to having sober monitors, and we will also provide snacks and water for all guests. Attendance will not exceed 190, and the event will run from 10:00PM to 2:00 AM. Jason Chapis, Ryan Bush, Everett Graves and Nick Enders will be the social hosts for the event.'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||' ',180),
