(9871976,'Superbowl Pub Party',cast('2024-02-11 18:00' as date),cast('2024-02-11 23:30' as date),'Donovan''s Pub','Social',NULL,'DP','Join us for a Superbowl Party at the Pub. Come for the game, stay for the food! Free food will be catered by Chartwells and by Ray Brothers BBQ (RBQ). There will also be games and giveaways!'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'Co-Sponsored by the Office of Student Involvement and the Shaw Wellness Institute. ',240),
(9893676,'Lovin'' Bingo',cast('2024-02-16 20:00' as date),cast('2024-02-16 22:00' as date),'The Coop- O''Connor Campus Center, Coop TV Room','Social',NULL,'SAA','Get ready to feel the love at ''Lovin'' Bingo''!  Join us on Friday, Feb. 16th at 8 pm in the Coop TV room for a heartwarming evening filled with fun, laughter, and incredible prizes.  Indulge in delectable delights from Royal India Grill (''RIG'') as you try your luck for a chance to win a huggable 6ft Teddy Bear, Amazon Echo Dot, Keurig K-Mini, and adorable LEGO flowers.  Love is the name of the game, and we can''t wait to share the joy with you!',260),
(9893695,'Casino Night',cast('2024-02-17 20:00' as date),cast('2024-02-17 23:00' as date),'The Coop- O''Connor Campus Center, Coop TV Room','Social',NULL,'SAA','Roll the dice and place your bets!  Join us for an unforgettable Casino Night on February 17th, from 8pm to 11pm. The excitement awaits with classic games like poker and blackjack, and delicious delights from Oliveri''s!  Stay tuned for a chance to win fantastic prizes, including town gift cards. Ante up for a night of thrills and good times! ',200),
(9934147,'Movie Night',cast('2024-02-16 23:00' as date),cast('2024-02-17 00:30' as date),'Hamilton Theater','Social',NULL,'SAA','Y''all voted and we listened!  Get ready for an unforgettable movie night at the Hamilton Movie Theater on February 16th at 11:00 PM. We''re bringing Legally Blonde to the big screen by popular demand!  Don''t miss out on this fan-favorite flick! ',450),
(9954417,'Barbie On Ice',cast('2024-02-24 21:00' as date),cast('2024-02-24 23:00' as date),'Class of 1965 Arena','Social',NULL,'SAA','Get ready to glide into a magical world with Barbie on Ice!  Join us on February 24th, 2024, at Class of 1965 Arena from 9pm to 11pm for an enchanting evening filled with twirls, spins, and dazzling performances!  Don''t miss out on this unforgettable experience!  Plus, enjoy delicious pizza from Oliveri! ',525),
(9985327,'Ask A Catholic Priest Anything',cast('2024-02-28 18:00' as date),cast('2024-02-28 20:00' as date),'Reception Room - Garden Level','Spirituality','Religious/Spiritual','NC','The Hudson Newman Catholic Community invites everyone to our weekly Wednesday dinner featuring Fr. John Donovan. The theme this week will be ask a priest anything so come with your best questions and join us for italian food!',null),
(9986796,'Movie Night',cast('2024-03-02 23:00' as date),cast('2024-03-03 01:30' as date),'Hamilton Theater','Social',NULL,'SAA',' NEW DATE ALERT  Join us for a cinematic journey like no other at Hamilton Movie Theater!  Experience the epic continuation of Dune Part 2 at our midnight movie screening on Saturday, March 2nd at 11:00 PM.  Get ready for an unforgettable adventure!',525),
