(1213394,'Passover',cast('2017-04-10 12:00' as date),cast('2017-04-18 12:00' as date),'SAP','Spirituality',NULL,'HJU','Passover is the 8 day long festival which commemorates the exodus of the Jews from Egypt. During this time, Jewish people eat only non-leavened foods which are certified as Kosher for Passover, and this food tends to be more expensive and not found at any of the Hudson Dining Facilities in quantities or varieties that are sufficient. Considering that the meal plan at Hudson costs students $36 per day, our $16 per day is more than reasonable. This event fed around 50 people last year for a week and has a projected upward participation rate.',270),
(1227605,'CJU Other Events',cast('2017-01-27 12:00' as date),cast('2017-05-12 12:00' as date),'SAP','Spirituality',NULL,'HJU','Bagel Brunch: This event is community bonding at the Saperstein Center.  Surprisingly, attendance can top 100 and we unfortunately do run out of bagels some days.  Additionally, we serve a large number of non-Jews thus including the whole Hudson community.  In addition to Hudson students, we also serve a large number of the Hamilton community.'||chr(10)||'Havdalah: Havdalah is celebrating the end of the Sabbath (Shabbat).  We host a great group of community members to have a quick service with light food afterward. '||chr(10)||'Advertising: Costs to provide supplies to get the word out for the whole semesters events.',200),
(525927,'Gospelfest 2015: Byron Cage',cast('2015-02-27 19:00' as date),cast('2015-02-27 21:00' as date),'Memorial Chapel','Spirituality',NULL,'SGC','Byron Cage will perform with Sojourner''s Gospel Choir.  This event will be viewable on Hudson University Livestream.  View here: http://new.livestream.com/hudsonuniversity/gospelfest2015'||chr(10)||' ',450),
(691889,'Bonfire on the Old Golf Course',cast('2015-08-29 20:00' as date),cast('2015-08-29 21:00' as date),'Fire Pit Behind Stillman','Spirituality',NULL,'HCF','Come on by to a bonfire hosted by CCF for music, to meet new friends, and most importantly...S''MORES! Also, there will be a sky talk given by one of Hudson''s very own expert astronomy student',null),
(745137,'Night Hike',cast('2015-09-25 22:00' as date),cast('2015-09-25 22:45' as date),'Chapel Steps','Spirituality',NULL,'HCF',NULL||chr(10)||'CCF will be hosting another Night Hike with glowsticks through the Hudson hiking trails starting at 10 PM Friday evening. Join us for a time of exploring Hudson''s beautiful property and enjoying the night sky. Stick around after the hike to have a campfire and s''mores in the field of dreams'||chr(10)||'',225),
(898260,'Tuesday Night Bible Study With Dr. Nina Moore',cast('2016-02-23 17:00' as date),cast('2016-02-23 18:30' as date),'Hudson Memorial Chapel','Spirituality',NULL,'UC','Join Dr. Nina Moore in the Chapel basement as she steps outside of her role as a Hudson faculty member. She will join the Protestant Campus Ministry and share her faith, helping to spread the Word of the Lord through inspirational Bible-based insights.'||chr(10)||'Dr. Morre will use the story of Joseph to elucidate the Principles of Godly Living.'||chr(10)||'See you in the chapel basement for some great discussion and a wonderful meal catered by Curtain Call.',140),
