(1076999,'Fall 2016 Additional Model UN Conferences',cast('2017-01-12 12:00' as date),cast('2017-01-15 13:00' as date),'Lima, Peru','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'MUN','Hudson Model United Nations Society would like to attend HNMUNLA Conference (Harvard National Model United Nations Latin America) in Lima, Peru and send an additional three delegates to BarMUN Conference (Boston Area Model United Nations).',null),
