(8373350,'Novice Weekend',cast('2022-09-17 09:00' as date),cast('2022-09-17 16:30' as date),'Lathrop Hall, Lawrence Hall (Multiple Rooms)','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'DS','In partnership with Hobart and William Smith Colleges in Geneva, NY, the Hudson Debate Society is hosting our annual Novice Weekend! Join us for a crash course in all things British Parliamentary debate! Workshops, debate rounds, lectures, socializing and more! Please contact debatesociety@hudson.edu by September 13, 2022 if you''re interested. ',450),
(857315,'Boston Immersion Trip - Spring 2016',cast('2016-03-03 16:00' as date),cast('2016-03-05 16:00' as date),'Boston, MA','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'HTC','The Hudson Finance Club is proud to sponsor an immersion trip to Boston to visit bulge bracket investment banks and major financial firms. The goal of the trip will be to provide quality exposure to the finance industry, connect with alumni, and experience first-hand one of the largest markets in the world.',180),
(866367,'Africa Business Conference Harvard University',cast('2016-02-26 12:00' as date),cast('2016-02-28 13:00' as date),'Harvard University','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'AS','The Africa Buisness Conference at Harvard University is an annual confrence that brings together 1500 people intrested in learning about buisness and entrepreneurship on the continent.  This is the  18th Annual Africa Business Conference, scheduled to be held in Boston, MA from February 26th to February 28th, 2016.'||chr(10)||'The theme  for the buisness conference is "Unite.  Innovate.  Disrupt:  Homegrown models for Africa''s prosperity" . Despite the media''s focus on the challenges in Africa,this years conference would like to celebrate the progress Africa has made over the years. During this year''s conference, The harvard Africa Buisness Conference aims to celebrate and promote awareness of existing innovative solutions that have been deployed in Africa as well as motivating  attendees to create more innovative solutions to overcome the challenges in Africa.'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||' ',550),
(866558,'Democracy Matters Spring 2016 Budget',cast('2016-01-26 12:30' as date),cast('2016-01-26 13:00' as date),'Coop TV Room','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'DM','Democracy Matters is a group on Hudson''s campus that strives to mitigate the effects of big money in politics. We are asking for funds for a number of events and other various programs that will spur more interest in our group and help achieve our goals.',null),
