(1032806,'Hudson International Community Brown Bag Series',cast('2016-09-22 12:15' as date),cast('2016-09-22 12:15' as date),'ALANA','Cultural',NULL,'HIC','Hudson International Community Brown Bags promote discussions on issues related to international student life at Hudson. We hope to engage international students as well as the larger Hudson community on issues such as identity, cultural differences, and racism that international students face. The experiences of international students are often underrepresented in larger campus conversations. Through the brown bags, we hope to create campus awareness on these issues and provide a space for international students to share their experiences.',200),
(1032807,'Hudson International Community Brown Bag Series',cast('2016-10-06 12:15' as date),cast('2016-10-06 12:15' as date),'ALANA','Cultural',NULL,'HIC','Hudson International Community Brown Bags promote discussions on issues related to international student life at Hudson. We hope to engage international students as well as the larger Hudson community on issues such as identity, cultural differences, and racism that international students face. The experiences of international students are often underrepresented in larger campus conversations. Through the brown bags, we hope to create campus awareness on these issues and provide a space for international students to share their experiences.',200),
