(181439,'Why Does God Matter to YOU?',cast('2012-10-16 19:00' as date),cast('2012-10-16 20:00' as date),'Memorial Chapel - Garden Level',NULL,'Religious/Spiritual','HCF','An Interfaith "Big Day" event where Christian students share why they beleive in God and how that faith has changed their lives.CCF is sponsoring a panel of students presenting on how they came to put their faith in Christ or one aspect of their life that has changed because of their faith. There will be time for questions afterwards. Dinner from Oliveri''s will be provided. ',450),
(185960,'Disney Princess Movie Night!',cast('2012-10-12 17:00' as date),cast('2012-10-13 10:00' as date),'Hamilton Bible Fellowship',NULL,'Religious/Spiritual','UC','University Church will be holding it''s first ever Disney Princess Night which will include Disney movies, baking, and other fun stuff! We encourage anyone to come who is interested. Cookies, childhood classics, and great friends will make this an event you won''t want to miss!',250),
