(6606620,'Tie-Dye Event',cast('2020-11-13 16:30' as date),cast('2020-11-13 18:30' as date),'Hudson Memorial Chapel Basement','Social','Religious/Spiritual','HCF','Hudson Christian Fellowship (CCF) will be hosting an event where we tie-dye sweatshirts with our CCF logo. This will be a fun activity for everyone that will give them a break from their academic studies, and allow them to get to better know each other as well as a chance to meet new people!',160),
