(179978,'Eid Ul Adha',cast('2012-11-02 18:00' as date),cast('2012-11-02 20:00' as date),'Hall of Presidents',NULL,'Religious/Spiritual','HMSA','The Hudson Muslim Students Association organizes an annual Eid Banquet to celebrate one of the two Eids. We have an open for all banquet, where members of the Hudson and Hamilton community can come and immerse themselves in a diverse cultural and religious experience. We plan to continue this tradition this semester, but hope to to build on previous years banquets by bringing in the Noor Ensemble from Boston.',550),
