(4957724,'Parent''s Weekend Brunch!',cast('2019-09-21 10:00' as date),cast('2019-09-21 11:00' as date),'Tri Delta House','Fundraising',NULL,'DDD','All Tri Delta members and their families are welcome! Tickets to enter are $7 (members must pay). Food will be served by our very own chef Eric, including eggs, hashbrowns, fruit, juices, and coffee! There will be raffles for fun gifts and all the proceeds go to St. Jude Children''s Research Hospital! Raffle tickets are 1 for $1, 5 for $4, and 10 for $7. ',300),
