(5086733,'Kappa Kickball',cast('2019-11-10 17:00' as date),cast('2019-11-10 19:00' as date),'Sanford Field House','Athletics',NULL,'KKG','This is an annual event Kappa Kappa Gamma holds. We reserve the Sanford Field House and are currently in contact with the athletic facility liaisons. Kappa Kickball is a campus-wide event where we encourage students to signup in teams of 6-8. The event usually runs for about 2 hours, with the teams competing against eachother. We have music and t-shirts for the event! We will be using a donation link with which students (and alumni) can make contributions. The donations will go towards both Reading is Fundamental (Kappa''s national philanthropy organization) and Kappa Nationals. We will also welcome donations at the door and will have a "team fee." ',700),
