(954525,'3 v. 3 Charity Basketball Tournament',cast('2016-09-24 12:00' as date),cast('2016-09-24 15:00' as date),'Huntington Gymnasium','Athletics',NULL,'BDS','The Blue Diamond Society will coordinate and host a 3 v. 3 basketball tournament to raise money for a charity of our choice. We will table to get participants and have a suggested donation to play. Additionally, students can donate money without playing in the tournament. The tournament will be help on a weekend in Huntington Gym and the winners will receive gift cards to restaurants in downtown Hamilton. ',120),
