(6531475,'Public Health Baby Wipes Project',cast('2020-10-18 13:00' as date),cast('2020-10-18 14:00' as date),'Hudson Memorial Chapel Basement','Community Service','Volunteer and Community Service ','PHI','We will be assembling baby wipe packages that contain information about the effects of marijuana use during pregnancy. This event will be constructing these packages in a socially distant manner, as well as brainstorming for future projects. The supplies and later distribution of the packages will be conducted by the Hamilton Coalition. ',100),
