(361012,'CAB Presents: CollegeHumor LIVE!',cast('2014-03-06 20:00' as date),cast('2014-03-06 21:30' as date),'Hudson Memorial Chapel',NULL,'Theater','SAA','CollegeHumor escapes the Internet to perform a live comedy show for Hudson! Featuring the lovable comedy duo Jake and Amir, the fan-favorite Streeter Seidell, and a few other *mystery guests* from the CollegeHumor staff, this show is certainly not one to miss. Click the following link for a personal promotion from the comedians themselves:  http://www.collegehumor.com/video/6927017/collegehumor-live-tour-promo',500),
(383937,'Taming of the Shrew',cast('2014-04-17 18:00' as date),cast('2014-04-19 21:00' as date),'Merrill House Lawn',NULL,'Theater','MAT','Taming of the Shrew is a comedy by William Shakespeare about the themes of love and marriage. Performances are being held on Wednesday, April 18; Thursday, April 17; and Saturday, April 19.',225),
(410212,'Taming of the Shrew',cast('2014-04-18 18:00' as date),cast('2014-04-18 19:00' as date),'Merrill House Lawn',NULL,'Theater','MAT','Performances of Shakespeare''s comedy, Taming of the Shrew, will be held on Merrill House Lawn.'||chr(10)||'In the case of rain, the show will be held in the HOP.'||chr(10)||'The show runs approximately 1:45 with an additional 5 minute intermission.',null),
