(232472,'24 Hour Burn',cast('2013-03-22 08:00' as date),cast('2013-03-23 20:30' as date),'Golden Auditorium',NULL,'Theater','MAT','Masque and Triangle''s 24 Hour Burn!  For the first twelve hours writers write the scripts and cast their shows.  For the next tweve, actors memorize lines and directors direct the scenes.  At 8 PM on Saturday, we put on a show all done in 24 hours!',425),
