(325730,'Musical One Night Stand',cast('2013-09-27 20:00' as date),cast('2013-09-27 20:00' as date),'Hall of Presidents',NULL,'Theater','MAT',NULL||chr(10)||'This semester, Masque and Triangle will be hosting its FIRST EVER MUSICAL ONE NIGHT STAND! A One Night Stand is a fun, low-commitment theater event in which actors and directors rehearse for three hours, immediately followed by a script-in-hand performance. This ONS, however, will feature exclusively musical numbers! No experience is necessary, and this is a totally casual and fun way to participate in or watch some theater. '||chr(10)||'The ONS will take place on Friday, September 27th in the Hall of Presidents in James C. Hudson Hall, with rehearsal beginning at 5:00 PM and the performance at 8:00. To participate, please email emcgrath@hudson.edu answering these questions by Monday, September 23rd:'||chr(10)||'1. Would you like to direct or sing?'||chr(10)||'2. What is your mailbox number?'||chr(10)||'The following questions are for performers only:'||chr(10)||'3. What voice part do you sing? If you do not know, just note whether your voice is relatively high or low compared to other people of your gender.'||chr(10)||'4. If you would like to sing, are you also interested in dancing? Please note your level of dance ability.'||chr(10)||'5. Do you prefer a solo, duet, small group or large group/ensemble piece?'||chr(10)||'We hope to see you all there as performers or audience members!',300),
(3279558,'Parents Night Out',cast('2019-03-22 16:00' as date),cast('2019-03-22 18:30' as date),'Delta Delta Delta House','Community Service','Volunteer and Community Service ','CPC','Members from Kappa Kappa Gamma, Gamma Phi Beta, and Delta Delta Delta will be working together through the Panhellenic Association to host a volunteer based event to care for faculty member''s children during the faculty tunk on March 22nd.',200),
