(856670,'A Cappella Benefit Concert',cast('2016-01-29 20:00' as date),cast('2016-01-29 21:30' as date),'Hudson Memorial Chapel','Arts',NULL,'SAA','COME SEE All of Hudson''s a cappella groups perform together, in a glorious collective set! Doors open at 8pm, Friday, January 29th. Tickets will be sold in the Coop and at the Chapel doors upon entry to the concert. All ticket proceeds are going to benefit Madison County Gives, an umbrella organization which provides hope, health and community through various charitable partnerships throughout Madison County. Co-sponsored by CAB and The Konosioni Honor Society, in conjunction with the Hudson Thirteen, Swinging Gates, Resolutions, Dischords and Mantiphondrakes.',240),
