(518073,'CABC Internship Showcase',cast('2015-03-14 16:30' as date),cast('2015-03-14 17:30' as date),'Batza Meeting Room, 560 Case Library','Arts',NULL,'HWIB','Hudson Asia Business Club is presenting a Internship Showcase and Coffee Hour Networking Session. There will be student mentors (junior and senior students) sharing internship experience, tips and advice with freshman and sophomore students. Student speakers have various career interests, such as investment banking, financial services, commercial banking, management consulting and auditing. Attend this networking event to engage with other students regarding their summer internship experiences. Food and beverages will be served.',500),
