(772308,'Mantiphondrakes Family Weekend Concert',cast('2015-10-30 18:00' as date),cast('2015-10-30 18:00' as date),'Donovan''s Pub','Arts',NULL,'MANTI','The Mantiphondrakes present their annual Family Weekend a Cappella concert on Friday, October 30th! Come to Donovan''s Pub in the JC Hudson Student Union to experience a night with the Mantis, featuring the on-stage debut of our five new members. You''ll hear a fantastic variety of music ranging from Sufjan Stevens to the Hobbit Soundtrack to the Queen B herself, Beyonce. There''s no better, more chill way to spend your Friday evening. The Mantis hope to see you there.',600),
(883302,'Amelie',cast('2016-02-20 17:00' as date),cast('2016-02-20 19:00' as date),'Golden Auditorium, Little Hall','Arts',NULL,'HFS','Join the Hudson Film Society for an evening filled with laughter. Amelie is the story of a shy waitress who attempts to improve the lives of those around her while dealing with her own isolation. The film was awarded best film at the European Film Awards and was nominated for five Academy Awards. '||chr(10)||'A link to the trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B-uxeZaM-VM',280),
(458903,'Montreal Trip',cast('2014-10-11 06:00' as date),cast('2014-10-13 22:45' as date),'Montreal','Arts',NULL,'FC','French Club leaders are looking to take a group of 29 students to spend their October Break (10/11-10/13) to the French-speaking city of Montreal, Quebec exploring its historic, linguistic, cultural, and environmental features. Students studying French and those interested in learning more about French/Francophone culture will be exposed to the diverse historical, linguistic, and cultural aspects of the City of Mary. French is the citys official language and is spoken by 56.9% of the population, providing an immersive non-academic environment for students to work on their French at any skill level in a real-world context while also learning more about Montreals unique culture. The trip will be aimed at students taking French or participating in French Club but will be open to the whole campus.',null),
(1032792,'Prisca DM Rodriguez',cast('2016-09-27 11:30' as date),cast('2016-09-27 12:00' as date),'WMST','Arts',NULL,'LASO','The Latin American Student Organization (LASO), in conjunction with Sisters of the Round Table (SORT) has invited Prisca Dorcas Mojica Rodriguez to come and speak during the 2016 Fall semester for Hispanic Heritage Month celebration.',550),
(564200,'Hudson Ballet Company Classes',cast('2015-02-03 19:30' as date),cast('2015-02-03 21:00' as date),'Huntington 303','Arts',NULL,'BALLET','Hudson Ballet Company provides classes taught by Paris Wilcox, a former principal dancer with Kansas City Ballet for students of all levels. The classes help develop students technique, flexibility, and strength. Classes take place Tuesday and Thursday.',330),
(573188,'CAMPVS DJ FEATURING VICETONE',cast('2015-02-26 21:00' as date),cast('2015-02-27 00:00' as date),'Palace Theater','Arts',NULL,'SAA','VICETONE to headline this semester''s Campvs DJ event!!'||chr(10)||'The Hudson Activities Board is proud to present another fantastic Campvs DJ event, following last year''s success with Cash Cash!'||chr(10)||'Thursday, February 26th at the Palace Theater!'||chr(10)||'ABOUT CAMPUS DJ:As the only nationwide search for the top collegiate DJs, Campus DJ is an authentic platform for students and universities to participate in an exciting national competition with huge prizing. Come see the best college DJs battle it out for their chance of being crowned the best college DJ in the country! To participate in the Hudson Battle, sign up at www.campusdj.com, and get your friends to vote! ',525),
(582760,'MandT Semester Events',cast('2015-01-19 12:00' as date),cast('2015-05-11 12:00' as date),'Hudson University','Arts',NULL,'MAT','This event includes all of MandT events for the semester. This includes Fringe Festival, two One Night Stands, one 24-Hour Burn, Cabaret, and a End of the Year Banquet. We have these every spring semester. '||chr(10)||'Total BAC money request: $3,345 (a budget can be provided). ',1000),
