(779334,'Student Theater: 24-Hour Burn presented by Masque and Triangle',cast('2015-10-24 19:00' as date),cast('2015-10-24 19:30' as date),'Donovan''s Pub','Arts',NULL,'MAT','Come watch your fellow theater-loving students put on a show at the 24-Hour Burn! Students will have 24 hours to write scenes and prepare to perform them through collaboration of student directors and actors. Scenes are usually extremely funny, amusing and original! The performance will be at 7 PM at Donovan''s Pub. Come out to support student theater on Hudson''s campus!!',190),
