(1025780,'MERASI-Master Musicans of Rajasthan',cast('2016-10-03 18:00' as date),cast('2016-10-03 19:30' as date),'Hudson Memorial Chapel','Cultural',NULL,'SACC','The event will showcase the talents of Merasi, a musical group from Rajasthan, India. This group performs traditional Rajasthani folk music of the Merasi tradition. There will be a live performance by the group followed by dinner for the audience and the group.',null),
