(1136045,'Interfaith Dinner',cast('2017-03-09 18:00' as date),cast('2017-03-09 19:00' as date),'Chapel Basement','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'NC','The Interfaith Dinners are an opportunity for students to come together, talk about their different beliefs and share a meal. Each dinner has a theme and discussion of this theme is co-led by members from two different Chaplaincy groups. This discussion-based style allows students who attend to participate during the dinner. These dinners have been extremely successful in the past.',null),
