(200064,'Cookout for Lakota Kids',cast('2012-11-14 17:00' as date),cast('2012-11-14 18:30' as date),'Coop TV Room',NULL,'Volunteer and Community Service ','NAIS','As a part of Native Heritage Month Celebrations, NASA will be hosting "Cookout for Lakota Kids." A BBQ event that we hope to hold on November 14th in the COOP. There will be Holy Smokes BBQ and free admission, although we will also be collecting suggested donations to go towards the COVE fund for the alternative break trip to the Pine Ridge Reservation in South Dakota.',null),
