(1248466,'University Church Board Game Night',cast('2017-02-16 21:00' as date),cast('2017-02-17 00:00' as date),'Interfaith House','Social',NULL,'UC','Enjoy a night of fellowship and fun with board games and dessert every Thursday, 9pm until midnight, at Interfaith House (104 Broad Street). Typical favorites include games like Avalon, Settlers of Catan, Blokus, Scrabble, and more! Feel free to bring your own games, as well. ',null),
