(518026,'Midterm Study Break',cast('2015-03-08 19:00' as date),cast('2015-03-08 20:00' as date),'Hall of Presidents','Social',NULL,'SAA','A Midterm Study Break will be held in the Hall of Presidents for all students seeking stress relief on March 8th! Attendees will be invited to enjoy the jazz and rock stylings of Hudson student band No Standards, a collection of guitar, bass, drum, saxophone, keyboard and trumpet!  Fresh pizza and mozz sticks from Oliveri''s will be served while students jam out together.',null),
(519757,'A Night of Sisterly Love',cast('2014-11-08 20:00' as date),cast('2014-11-09 10:00' as date),'The Center for Women''s Studies','Social','Movie/Film','SRT','Sister of the Round Table Presents: "A Night of Sisterly Love" this Saturday at the Center for Women''s Studies.'||chr(10)||'There will be food, games, movies, music and great people. SORT will provide sleeping bags, so bring your pillows and lovely faces!',null),
(539355,'Hug-A-Thon Study Break',cast('2014-12-14 18:00' as date),cast('2014-12-14 19:30' as date),'Case Library Batza Room 560','Social',NULL,'BROS','Brothers wants to dismantle the fear of men of color and gender stereotypes that men do not talk about their feelings, especially in light of recent global, national, and campus events.We will offer free coffee, hot chocolate,tea, slices,wings, snacks, and hugs. It will be on Sunday Dec. 14 in Case Library Room 560 from 6:00pm until 7:30pm. Brandon Doby will play vibrational, soul music. ',null),
(623090,'Welcome Back BBQ',cast('2015-08-27 17:00' as date),cast('2015-08-27 18:00' as date),'Academic Quad','Social',NULL,'SAA','The Welcome Back BBQ, held on the half-day of classes, is a time for members of the Hudson community to come together and enjoy Holy Smokes BBQ. This event is meant to spark excitement for the upcoming semester and create an opportunity for first-years and upperclassmen to get to know each other, all the while enjoying delicious food on a beautiful night at Hudson. ',null),
(634254,'Konosioni Field Day',cast('2015-08-26 13:00' as date),cast('2015-08-26 14:30' as date),'The Old Golf Course (Field of Dreams)','Social',NULL,'THS','Konosioni Field Day is a Hudson tradition for incoming first-year students. All Konosioni members will be available supply food and run games on the Old Golf Course (Field of Dreams) to build dorm cohesion and get people to meet eachother in a fun setting. Dorms will compete in challenges like tug of war, capture the flag and other large team games.',null),
(6878561,'Junior and Senior Care Packages',cast('2021-02-05 11:30' as date),cast('2021-02-05 13:30' as date),'The Mat at Parker Commons','Social',NULL,'SAA','The 2021 and 2022 Class Councils have put together care packages for members of the councils to pick up and enjoy from Parker Commons between 11:30 and 1:30. Packages are first come, first serve as there is a limited amount. ',null),
(7026463,'Open Art-Making with the Senior Honor Society',cast('2021-04-06 20:00' as date),cast('2021-04-06 21:00' as date),'Hall of Presidents','Arts','Volunteer and Community Service ','THS','Join the Senior Honor Society Class of 2021 and 2022 to make some original artwork! Follow a guided lesson from a Hudson art professor in one side of the room or hang out and listen to music and work on independent pieces on the other side of the room. There will be Senior Honor Society members floating around to help guide you on technique, help you come up with ideas, and make art alongside you.',null),
(723331,'MIDNIGHT MOVIE! Maze Runner: Scorch Trials',cast('2015-09-18 23:45' as date),cast('2015-09-18 23:45' as date),'Hamilton Movie Theater','Social',NULL,'SAA','CAB Take Two presents this semester''s first Midnight Movie, Maze Runner: Scorch Trials! Come with your HUES Card for free admission, popcorn, and slices! '||chr(10)||'Synopsis: Transported to a remote fortified outpost, Thomas and his fellow teenage Gladers find themselves in trouble after uncovering a diabolical plot from the mysterious and powerful organization WCKD. With help from a new ally, the Gladers stage a daring escape into the Scorch, a desolate landscape filled with dangerous obstacles and crawling with the virus-infected Cranks. The Gladers only hope may be to find the Right Hand, a group of resistance fighters who can help them battle WCKD.',null),
(7411046,'LASO Loteria Night',cast('2021-09-24 20:00' as date),cast('2021-09-24 21:00' as date),'Donovan''s Pub','Cultural',NULL,'LASO','Join LASO in Loteria Night on September 24th from 6:00 pm-8:00 pm! We will have grand prizes like the Nintendo Switch, Mexican Candy Care Packages, and more! Loteria is a game of chance similar to the American game Bingo, but using a deck of cards with images and is a lot of fun to play with friends and community!',null),
(7583171,'Summer Experience Student Panel',cast('2021-12-02 17:00' as date),cast('2021-12-02 18:30' as date),'COOP Conference Room','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'HGHC','Meet GHC Seniors with summer experience in the global public health field. Learn about on-campus and off-campus opportunities for research, internships, and full-time positions.',null),
(7583175,'Fall 2021 Public Health Seminar: Collaborative Research with the Bwindi Community Hospital in Uganda',cast('2021-11-09 17:00' as date),cast('2021-11-09 19:00' as date),'Batza Room, Case Library','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'HGHC','We are excited for our Fall 2021 Public Health Seminar: Collaborative Research with the Bwindi Community Hospital in Uganda. Professor Frank Frey will be joining us to discuss a decade worth of public health research and ways to get involved with the Global Public and Environmental Health field inside and outside of the classroom. '||chr(10)||'Dinner will be catered by Rio Grande. RSVP here! ',null),
(7641075,'Teacher''s Day Dinner Celebration',cast('2021-12-08 18:30' as date),cast('2021-12-08 19:30' as date),'ALANA Cultural Center','Cultural',NULL,'HVS','Every year on the 20th of November, millions of people in Vietnam celebrate this day with flowers and gifts to express gratitude to some of the most important figures in their lives - their teachers. Recognizing that Teacher''s Day is a very important day in many cultures, Hudson Vietnamese Society (HVS) would like to invite students and teachers alike on campus to come and celebrate this special day together. There will be Vietnamese food served by New Century Viet at the event. Additionally, there will be cards and flowers for students to give to their professors the following days as a token of appreciation.',null),
(7680397,'Springo!',cast('2022-02-19 21:00' as date),cast('2022-02-19 23:00' as date),'Coop TV Room','Social',NULL,'SAA','RESCHEDULED FOR FEBRUARY 19TH!!'||chr(10)||'Like bingo, but with spring rolls and Chinese food! Come to the Coop TV Room for a chance to win awesome prizes.'||chr(10)||'Wear your masks!',null),
(779333,'ROCKY HORROR PICTURE SHOW MIDNIGHT MOVIE',cast('2015-10-23 23:45' as date),cast('2015-10-23 23:45' as date),'Hamilton Movie Theater','Social',NULL,'SAA','Let''s do the TIME WARP again!!! Our annual screening of ROCKY HORROR is this Friday, October 23rd! Admission is free with a HUES Card and SLICES will be served. ',null),
(800500,'Hudson Women in Business Coffee Hour Series',cast('2016-04-19 20:00' as date),cast('2016-04-19 20:00' as date),'Batza Room, Case Library','Group Business',NULL,'HWIB','This series involves monthly coffee hours to educate members on different aspects of the business industry. ',null),
(8035435,'Suture Event',cast('2022-04-13 18:30' as date),cast('2022-04-13 18:30' as date),'101 Ho','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'PVC','The Suture Event is hosted by the Pre-Veterinary club and Pre-Health Pathways. A veterinarian from a local clinic will come to Hudson University to demo the basic suturing techniques used ubiquitously in medicine. As the veterinarian demonstrates, students will have the opportunity to follow along on their individual suture kits and ask questions. ',null),
(821043,'Stone a Heathen',cast('2015-04-21 16:00' as date),cast('2015-04-21 17:00' as date),'Academic Quad','Community Service',NULL,'SASS','Support protection from religious discrimination by having some snacks and fun in the sun! Buy a t-shirt or some water balloons and stone your favorite heathens! All proceeds go to the Interfaith Alliance for protecting faith and freedom.',null),
(8374772,'New Student Club Meeting',cast('2022-09-22 18:00' as date),cast('2022-09-22 18:00' as date),'Ho 101','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'HUSPS','The meeting is aimed at retaining new students who have expressed interest in our club. We will discuss past events, upcoming events, and more ways to get involved.',null),
(874176,'Brothers Charity Week 2016',cast('2016-03-28 12:00' as date),cast('2016-04-01 22:45' as date),'Hudson University','Fundraising',NULL,'BROS','Brothers Charity Week is composed of several activities placed throughout the week, with the intent of raising money for the surrounding Hamilton community and/or a worthwhile, larger global charitable organization beginning March 28 until April 1, 2016.'||chr(10)||'On Monday, March 28, Brothers will start the week with a BBQ and Bake Sale supported by the Office of the Chaplains on the academic quad during lunchtime, in conjunction with a homemade bake sale occurring in the Coop.'||chr(10)||'On Tuesday, March 29, Brothers will have a video gaming tournament in conjunction with ResLife  and The Games Afoot at Donovans Pub at 7pm.'||chr(10)||'On Wednesday March 30, Brothers will host a basketball tournament with the aid of the Mens Basketball team and BDS at Huntington Gym at 7pm. '||chr(10)||'On Thursday March 31, Brothers will have a Karaoke night at Donovans Pub at 7pm. '||chr(10)||'On Friday April 1, the Brothers Charity Auction will take place at 6pm in the Hall of Presidents and our  fundraising party will begin at 10pm in the 80 Broad Street (subject to change). '||chr(10)||'All throughout the week, we will accept suggested donations at all events in addition to our Coop table, where the Bake Sale will be ongoing. We will be selling t-shirts throughout the week as well.',null),
(9044958,'13 Days of Green - Afternoon of Service (Wellness Passport Credit!)',cast('2023-04-14 13:30' as date),cast('2023-04-14 15:00' as date),'COVE Lounge - Lathrop 109','Community Service','Sustainability','COVE','Interested in getting outside for a good cause this spring? After the ENST Brown Bag, join us in giving back to your community through volunteering with local, environmentally-focused organizations. You we have the choice of getting your hands dirty with invasive plant removal, trail maintenance, garden preparation, or supporting the COVE Salvage Program by painting the donation boxes. Check out the community partners we will be supporting here:'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'Hudson Community Garden'||chr(10)||'Roger''s Environmental Education Center'||chr(10)||'Chenengo Trail Association'||chr(10)||'Spring Farm CARES Nature Sanctuary'||chr(10)||'COVE Salvage Program'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'Sign up here before Wednesday, April 12th!'||chr(10)||'Snacks provided, but please bring your own reusable water bottle.'||chr(10)||'Participants can also receive 2 hours of credit toward their PE Wellness Passport!'||chr(10)||'This event is co-sponsored by the Hudson Center for Outreach, Volunteerism, and Education as part of the Office of Sustainabilitys 13 Days of Green series leading up to Earth Day.',null),
(9580630,'Halloweekend@Donnies',cast('2023-11-03 23:00' as date),cast('2023-11-04 00:00' as date),'Donovan''s Pub','Social','Concert/Music','SAA','Free food, student DJ, and giveaways! ',null),
(9866839,'CWiB Coffee Hour #1',cast('2024-02-12 19:00' as date),cast('2024-02-12 20:00' as date),'Case Geyer 560 Batza Room','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'HWIB','Please join the Hudson Women in Business Organization for a monthly coffee hour to discuss different aspects of the field of business.  Meetings may include breakout sessions to discuss specific industries within the field of business, hearing tips from upperclassman who have experience in the business field, revising a resume or cover letter, speaking with alumni and established professions in the field of business, and more.  ',null),
(9880356,'Midnight Philosophy Society Meeting',cast('2024-04-20 22:00' as date),cast('2024-04-21 00:00' as date),'Donovan''s Pub','Social',NULL,'MPS','Midnight Philosophy is a vibrant community of inquisitive and curious students who are excited to explore diverse and relevant philosophical topics! We host welcoming student-to-student conversations about morality, society, religion, metaphysics, and epistemology. Our members are diverse in their beliefs, and we are open to absolutely anyone, with no philosophical experience or major declaration necessary. ',null),
(9954247,'QTPOC Presents: Baby Tate',cast('2024-03-01 22:00' as date),cast('2024-03-01 23:00' as date),'The MAT','Arts','Concert/Music','WHUR','Baby Tate is always evolving, fuelled by self-love and manifested dreams. The Atlanta-based musician''s sound remains expansive. Summery pop, passionate RandB, and hard-hitting hip-hop all coexist in a single body of work. ROYGBIV, Baby Tate''s debut album, saw her exerting complete creative autonomy as a singer, songwriter, rapper, producer, and engineerindependent skills she''s honed since she was a child. She''s released concept albums as well as unrestricted songs, all while emphasizing female empowerment and joy, as seen by her unified, yet varied 2020 EP After the Rain, which contains her viral, confidence-boosting hit "I Am." Twinged with influence from her southern roots, Baby Tate has a drawled-out rapping style that streamlines her rap persona to another level, gaining around 5 million monthly streams on Spotify.'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'Please join us for a night of party-banger music brought to you by Baby Tate!',null),
(593454,'Cabaret',cast('2015-02-26 19:00' as date),cast('2015-02-26 21:00' as date),'Brehmer Theater','Arts',NULL,'MAT',' The theme for this year''s musical theatre Cabaret is "Come Together Cabaret," which celebrates the Hudson community coming together to appreciate some feel-good songs despite the tension of last semester. So come join us in enjoying some great songs performed by lots of talented Hudson students at this year''s Cabaret!',null),
(722313,'Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid',cast('2015-09-12 17:00' as date),cast('2015-09-12 18:00' as date),'Golden Auditorium','Arts',NULL,'HFS','Come and see a classic Western with the Hudson Film Society! A tale of two men, their wild adventures, and remarkable friendship in the American frontier. Starring Paul Newman and Robert Redford. Running time is 1 hr 53 minutes. '||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'Trailer',null),
(781476,'The Hudson Thirteen and Swinging ''Gates Family Weekend Concert',cast('2015-10-30 19:00' as date),cast('2015-10-30 20:00' as date),'Chapel','Arts',NULL,'HT','Hudsons premier all-male and all-female acapella groups, The Hudson Thirteen and Swinging ''Gates, will take the chapel stage on Friday October 30th for their annual Family Weekend concert. Each groups preformance will feature soloists from the class of 2016 singing a mix of brand new songs and group classics as they celebrate their final Family Weekend. Tickets for the whole family can be purchased in Frank Dinning Hall and the Coop starting Monday October 26th. ',null),
(6571308,'Photo Editing Workshop',cast('2020-10-30 15:00' as date),cast('2020-10-30 16:00' as date),'DLMC Room','Arts',NULL,'PC','Are the colors a bit drab in your photo? Want to remove that annoying fly or person from your group pic? Then the Photo Club has the solution for you as we will be teaching you the essentials of photo editing in Photoshop! Adjust colors, merge photos, and create scenes that would be impossible otherwise. When you sign up, we''ll send an email on how to upload your photos so we can get started quickly.',null),
(821047,'Platoon',cast('2015-10-24 17:00' as date),cast('2015-10-24 18:00' as date),'Golden Auditorium, Little Hall','Arts',NULL,'HFS','Join the Hudson Film Society and see Oliver Stone''s harrowing tale of a platoon of soldiers as they encounter the stressors and chaos of combat. Based off of Stone''s own service, the film is the first major production to have been directed by a Vietnam veteran, perhaps contributing to his being awarded the 1986 Academy Award for best director. Running time is 2 hours.',null),
(8621946,'Jaboukie Young-White',cast('2022-12-02 20:00' as date),cast('2022-12-02 21:00' as date),'Hall of Presidents','Arts',NULL,'HSU','Hosted by Hudson Stand-Up, Jaboukie Young-White will perform for students in the Hall of Presidents. '||chr(10)||' ',null),
(935074,'Dancefest Hosts Auditions',cast('2016-04-03 13:00' as date),cast('2016-04-03 13:00' as date),'Ryan 212','Arts',NULL,'GDT','Come audition to be a Dancefest host this Sunday, April 3rd at 1pm in Ryan 212! ',null),
(945087,'Mantiphondrakes Fall Concert',cast('2016-11-11 19:00' as date),cast('2016-11-11 20:00' as date),'Memorial Chapel','Arts',NULL,'MANTI','Come to our Fall Concert! Featuring a diverse mix of covers of songs of artists, all in the Chapel on a Friday!',null),
(1025861,'South Asian Cultural Club Sponsored Cricket Tournament',cast('2016-10-01 14:00' as date),cast('2016-10-01 15:00' as date),'Whitnall Field','Athletics',NULL,'SACC','The SACC is planning to host a cricket match to expose the Hudson community to one of the most religiously followed sports on the Indian subcontinent.',null),
(1032791,'Inca Son Performance',cast('2016-09-21 18:00' as date),cast('2016-09-21 18:30' as date),'Brehmer Auditorium','Arts',NULL,'LASO','The Latin American Student Organization (LASO) has invited the Inca Son dance group to perform in honor of Hispanic Heritage Month (HHM) tentatively on September 21st.',null),
(1048027,'OASIS Brown Bag Series',cast('2016-10-17 11:30' as date),cast('2016-10-17 12:00' as date),'WMST','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'OASIS','OASIS is hosting two brown bags where we invite female Asian American scholars, writers, and professors to share about their research work and activism experience that revolve around Asian American literature, culture, representation, and Asian American feminist studies.',null),
(1119415,'Gospel Fest',cast('2017-02-17 19:00' as date),cast('2017-02-17 21:00' as date),'Hudson Memorial Chapel','Arts',NULL,'SGC','Hudson Universitys Gospel Fest is an annual two-hour choral performance featuring a special guest gospel artist along with Hudson Sojourners Gospel Choir and other choirs, such as the Chamber Singers. This year we will be bringing back Walt Whitman and the Soul Children of Chicago (SCC) to headline Gospel Fest 2017. Over the years, Gospel Fest has seen much success, hosting celebrated gospel artists/groups such as Kirk Franklin, Marvin Sapp, The Harlem Gospel Choir and Byron Cage. ',null),
(1283488,'Stories of the Prophet Series',cast('2017-04-06 19:00' as date),cast('2017-04-06 19:00' as date),'Chapel Basement','Spirituality','Religious/Spiritual','HMSA','The Muslim Student Association would like to have a series of events to raise awareness about Islam and dispel common myths and misunderstandings surrounding Islam. This series is also geared towards having a space for an open discussion about the different cultural, religious and moral aspects of Islam, and how differently they are perceived by people in different regions of the world. A series of three dinner discussions over the period of a month, these events would encourage interfaith learning by inviting different religious groups and discussing intersecting values and differences in thought.',null),
(168715,'Take Two: The Five-Year Engagement',cast('2012-09-15 22:00' as date),cast('2012-09-15 23:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','One year after meeting, Tom proposes to his girlfriend, Violet, but unexpected events keep tripping them up as they look to walk down the aisle together.'||chr(10)||'Jason Segel, Emily Blunt, and Chris Pratt; R; 124 min.; 2012.',null),
(194093,'Take Two: Brave',cast('2012-10-27 19:00' as date),cast('2012-10-27 20:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','Determined to make her own path in life, Princess Merida defies a custom that brings chaos to her kingdom. Granted one wish, Merida must rely on her bravery and her archery skills to undo a beastly curse.'||chr(10)||'Kelly Macdonald, Billy Connolly and Emma Thompson; Rated PG; 100 min.; 2012.',null),
(196932,'Take Two: The Dark Knight',cast('2012-11-02 22:00' as date),cast('2012-11-02 23:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','When Batman, Gordon and Harvey Dent launch an assault on the mob, they let the clown out of the box, the Joker, bent on turning Gotham on itself and bringing any heroes down to his level.'||chr(10)||'Christian Bale, Heath Ledger and Aaron Eckhart; Rate PG-13; 152 min.',null),
(200466,'Take Two: The Amazing Spider-Man',cast('2012-11-09 22:00' as date),cast('2012-11-10 00:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','Peter Parker finds a clue that might help him understand why his parents disappeared when he was young. His path puts him on a collision course with Dr. Curt Connors, his father''s former partner.'||chr(10)||'Andrew Garfield, Emma Stone and Rhys Ifans; PG-13; 136 min.'||chr(10)||'from imdb.com',null),
(205933,'Photography Club: First Meeting!',cast('2012-11-30 17:00' as date),cast('2012-11-30 17:30' as date),'Coop Conference Room',NULL,NULL,'PC','Come to our first ever Photography Club meeting! If you have any interest in joining the club, you should join us to learn about what our plans are for the remainder of this semester and next semester. Also, if you would like to run for an executive board position, it is important that you attend this first meeting.',null),
(228734,'Staff Meeting',cast('2013-02-21 19:00' as date),cast('2013-02-21 20:00' as date),'COOP Conference Room',NULL,NULL,'RAG','Come out and write for the Rag! During these meetings, we get together and throw out story ideas, generate articles, and have everyone volunteer to write whatever they''re interested in. These meetings are open and completely non-committed (unless you commit to a story.) '||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'Complimentary oxygen provided. ',null),
(230543,'CAB Take Two: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 2',cast('2013-02-23 19:00' as date),cast('2013-02-23 21:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two presents The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 2:'||chr(10)||'After the birth of Renesmee, the Cullens gather other vampire clans in order to protect the child from a false allegation that puts the family in front of the Volturi.'||chr(10)||'from imdb.com',null),
(244421,'CAB Take Two: Lincoln',cast('2013-03-22 22:00' as date),cast('2013-03-22 22:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents:'||chr(10)||'Zero Dark Thirty at 7:00PM and Lincoln at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, March 22nd, and again at opposite times on Saturday, March 23rd.'||chr(10)||'Zero Dark Thirty:'||chr(10)||'A chronicle of the decade-long hunt for al-Qaeda terrorist leader Osama bin Laden after the September 2001 attacks, and his death at the hands of the Navy S.E.A.L. Team 6 in May 2011.'||chr(10)||'Lincoln:'||chr(10)||'As the Civil War continues to rage, America''s president struggles with continuing carnage on the battlefield and as he fights with many inside his own cabinet on the decision to emancipate the slaves.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(281685,'CAB Take Two: Snitch',cast('2013-05-04 22:00' as date),cast('2013-05-04 22:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Presents:'||chr(10)||'Snitch (Fri 7pm and Sat 10pm):'||chr(10)||'A father goes undercover for the DEA in order to free his son who was imprisoned after being set up in drug deal.'||chr(10)||'Oz the Great and the Powerful (Fri 10pm and Sat 7pm):'||chr(10)||'A small-time magician is swept away to an enchanted land and is forced into a power struggle between three witches.',null),
(287425,'Yale IV 2013',cast('2013-10-04 10:15' as date),cast('2013-10-05 22:30' as date),'Yale University, New Haven, CY',NULL,'Volunteer and Community Service ','DS','Yale Intervarsity Parliamentary Debate Tournament 2013 is an international debate tournament that is held in the British Parliamentary style which will take place at Yale University in New Haven, Connecticut on Friday, October 4 and Saturday, October 5. '||chr(10)||'The tournament will consist of five preliminary rounds, followed by a varsity quarters break and a novice* final round. All rounds will be debated in the British Parliamentary style. This will be an excellent opportunity for teams to prepare for Worlds. The judging pool at the tournament will feature some of the best adjudicators available.',null),
(302819,'CAB Take Two: Monster''s University',cast('2013-10-04 22:00' as date),cast('2013-10-04 22:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents: Despicable Me 2 at 7:00PM and Monsters University at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Oct 4th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, Oct 5th.'||chr(10)||'Despicable Me 2 (Fri 7pm/Sat 10pm)'||chr(10)||'Gru is recruited by the Anti-Villain League to help deal with a powerful new super criminal.'||chr(10)||'Monster''s University (Fri 10pm/Sat 7pm)'||chr(10)||'A look at the relationship between Mike and Sulley during their days at Monsters University -- when they weren''t necessarily the best of friends.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(325353,'SORT Sleepover',cast('2013-11-08 20:00' as date),cast('2013-11-09 10:00' as date),'Center for Women''s Studies',NULL,NULL,'SRT','A Night of Sisterly Love sleepover will be  held on Friday November 8, 2013 from 8:00PM-10:00PM in the common area of The Womens Studies Center. The concept of the sleepover is that it is a night where members of the organization and our allies can partake in food, conversation, movies, and games. It also serves as an opportunity for the upperclassmen members of the organization to bond with the younger generation. With our records showing an average of 28 individuals per SORT meeting, and given the success of this event in previous years, we are confident that this event will bring in more members. This event will also help all members become more comfortable with the Center for Womens Studies.',null),
(3279355,'Inaugural Meeting',cast('2019-03-27 16:15' as date),cast('2019-03-27 16:15' as date),'Lawrence 304','Social',NULL,'HODC','The Hudson Open Discussion club, during its first meeting, will welcome new members into the organization. The Club will also go through basic administrative duties. ',null),
(338845,'CAB Take Two Saturday Matinee: American Pie',cast('2013-12-07 14:00' as date),cast('2013-12-07 15:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','NEW THIS YEAR!'||chr(10)||'CAB Take Two presents Saturday Matinee! Saturday (Dec 7th) 2:00 pm, the classic comedy American Pie will be shown in Love Auditorium.'||chr(10)||'American Pie (starring: Jason Biggs, Chris Klein, Thomas Ian Nicholas)'||chr(10)||'Four teenage boys enter a pact to lose their virginity by prom night.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(365707,'CAB Take Two: The Best Man Holiday',cast('2014-02-01 22:00' as date),cast('2014-02-01 23:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Presents:'||chr(10)||'The Best Man Holiday at 8:00 PM and The Fifth Estate at 10:00 PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Jan 31th.'||chr(10)||'On Saturday Feb 1st: The Fifth Estate at 7:00PM and The Best Man Holiday at 10:00 PM'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'The Best Man Holiday (Fri 8:00PM and Sat 10:00PM)'||chr(10)||'When college friends reunite after 15 years over the Christmas holidays, they discover just how easy it is for long-forgotten rivalries and romances to be reignited.'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'The Fifth Estate (Fri 10:00 PM and sat 7:00PM)'||chr(10)||'A dramatic thriller based on real events that reveals the quest to expose the deceptions and corruptions of power that turned an Internet upstart into the 21st century''s most fiercely debated organization.',null),
(403612,'CAB Take Two: Her',cast('2014-03-29 19:00' as date),cast('2014-03-29 20:15' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Presents:'||chr(10)||'About Time at 7:00PM and Her at 10:00 PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Mar 28th.'||chr(10)||'On Saturday Mar 29th: Her at 7:00PM and About Time at 10:00 PM'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'About Time (Fri 7:00PM and Sat 10:00PM)'||chr(10)||'Starring  Domhnall Gleeson, Rachel McAdams, Bill Nighy'||chr(10)||'At the age of 21, Tim discovers he can travel in time and change what happens and has happened in his own life. His decision to make his world a better place by getting a girlfriend turns out not to be as easy as you might think.'||chr(10)||'Her (Fri 10:00 PM and sat 7:00PM)'||chr(10)||'Starring Joaquin Phoenix, Amy Adams, Scarlett Johansson '||chr(10)||'A lonely writer develops an unlikely relationship with his newly purchased operating system that''s designed to meet his every need.',null),
(404089,'Video Series - Why Democracy Matters: "Inequality for All"',cast('2014-04-10 16:30' as date),cast('2014-04-10 17:30' as date),'Lathrop 212',NULL,'Movie/Film','DM','Why should students care about the state of politics in America, or dysfunction in the government? In a series of three films, apolitical nonprofit Democracy Matters attempts to get to the root causes of everything from student debt to economic- and gender-based inequality, covering environmental spoilage and racial tensions along the way. April 10: Inequality for All April 17: The Corporation April 24: Priceless',null),
(464297,'CAB Take Two movie: 22 Jump Street',cast('2014-09-12 19:00' as date),cast('2014-09-12 20:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Presents:'||chr(10)||'22 Jump Street at 7:00PM and Neighbors at 10:00 PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Sep 12th.'||chr(10)||'On Saturday Sep 13th: Neighbors at 7:00PM and 22 Jump Street at 10:00 PM'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'22 Jump Street (Fri 7:00PM and Sat 10:00PM) Click Here for the Trailer of 22 Jump Street!'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'Starring: Channing Tatum, Jonah Hill'||chr(10)||'After making their way through high school (twice), big changes are in store for officers Schmidt and Jenko when they go deep undercover at a local college.'||chr(10)||'Neighbors (Fri 10:00 PM and sat 7:00PM) Watch Neighbors trailer now!'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'Starring: Zac Efron, Seth Rogen, Rose Byrne'||chr(10)||'A couple with a newborn baby face unexpected difficulties after they are forced to live next to a fraternity house.',null),
