(593943,'SORT General Meeting "Solidarity Amongst Women of Color"',cast('2015-02-25 17:00' as date),cast('2015-02-25 18:00' as date),'WMST','Cultural',NULL,'SRT','This event is a part of Sister''s of the Round Table''s annual Africana Women''s Week(s). During our general meeting we will discuss where the term women of color originated and what it means to be a woman of color in contemporary times and on the Hudson campus. This event is in collaboration with OASIS and Women Studies. Food will be provided. ',null),
