(772318,'Konosioni Open Application Coffee Hour',cast('2015-12-01 21:00' as date),cast('2015-12-01 22:00' as date),'Case Guyer, 560 Batza Room','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'THS','The Konosioni (Kono) Society hosts two annual coffee hours specifically targeted for Juniors who are interested in applying or learning more about Kono''s mission, goals, and membership application process. This is a great time for interested juniors to meet all of the current kono members and ask any questions or get first hand information about Kono from a variety of people. The purpose of having two coffee hours is to reach as many interested juniors as possible. We are a campus full of busy people, so we want to ensure that we are being inclusive throughout our entire application outreach process and accommodate for potential conflict. We only host two events because we believe that is the most fiscally reasonable and responsible. This proposal is for one coffee hour that we would like to have the day after applications open for the entire junior class.',null),
