(9514573,'Meditation Night Hike',cast('2023-10-12 18:45' as date),cast('2023-10-12 19:30' as date),'Hudson Chapel House','Athletics',NULL,'HIKE','We are glad to announce that our next hiking club event will be on next Thursday October 12th at 6:45pm. After meeting outside of Frank, We will be walking up to the Chapel House where we will have a meditation session at 7pm before continuing up onto the XC trails for a night hike! Were looking forward to seeing you all there!'||chr(10)||'Bring a flashlight or headlamp if you have one, although a phone flashlight is probably good enough. '||chr(10)||'Join the Hiking Club Groupme here for up-to-date information on hiking club events-  https://groupme.com/join_group/89114067/leHjjOU5',null),
