(9642606,'Festivus (for the Rest of Us)',cast('2023-12-02 14:00' as date),cast('2023-12-02 17:00' as date),'Coop TV Room','Cultural','Religious/Spiritual','SASS','Inspired by Seinfeld, Festivus (for the rest of us) is a secular holiday that aims to create a space away from the religiosity and consumerism of other winter holidays. We will have a large aluminum pole, an airing of the grievances, feats of strength, and a hearty meal, as tradition.'||chr(10)||'The event will take place Saturday, December 2nd, in the Coop TV Room from 2-4. Everyone is welcome, so please drop by!',null),
(9866807,'Coffee Hour #3',cast('2024-04-01 19:00' as date),cast('2024-04-01 19:00' as date),'Case Geyer 560 Batza Room','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'HWIB','Please join the Hudson Women in Business Organization for a monthly coffee hour to discuss different aspects of the field of business.  Meetings may include breakout sessions to discuss specific industries within the field of business, hearing tips from upperclassman who have experience in the business field, revising a resume or cover letter, speaking with alumni and established professions in the field of business, and more. ',null),
(9866811,'Coffee Hour #2',cast('2024-03-04 19:00' as date),cast('2024-03-04 20:00' as date),'Case Geyer 560 Batza Room','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'HWIB','Please join the Hudson Women in Business Organization for a monthly coffee hour to discuss different aspects of the field of business.  Meetings may include breakout sessions to discuss specific industries within the field of business, hearing tips from upperclassman who have experience in the business field, revising a resume or cover letter, speaking with alumni and established professions in the field of business, and more. ',null),
(9949002,'Craft and Create: An Afternoon With LEGO and Circuits',cast('2024-02-16 14:30' as date),cast('2024-02-16 16:00' as date),'McGregory 314, Hamilton, New York','Social','Sustainability','HTT',NULL||chr(10)||'HELLO ROBOTICISTS,'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'GOOD AFTERNOON! Hope your guys'' weeks are going great! Just a quick reminder that our meeting will be on Friday 2:30-onwards at McGregory 314. Same place. Same time. This week, we''re inviting you and your friends to a laid-back yet engaging session where the simplicity of LEGO meets the innovation and the interactivity of Circuit Playgrounds.'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'',null),
(735202,'French Club Coffee Hour',cast('2015-11-11 16:15' as date),cast('2015-11-11 17:00' as date),'Lawrence Hall 2nd floor','Cultural',NULL,'FC','Come enjoy a presentation on a Francophone topic with snacks included such as croissants every month with a Francophone film screening to follow that weekend.',null),
(404759,'French Club Coffee Hour',cast('2014-09-17 16:15' as date),cast('2014-09-17 16:15' as date),'Lawrence 205',NULL,NULL,'FC','French Club Coffee Hours are meant to promote French language and culture in a non-academic environment. At each of the four Coffee Hours, French Club leaders give a presentation on an aspect of French culture, for example student life at French universities, followed by questions and vocabulary relevant to the topic to encourage conversation amongst participants. These questions are broad enough for all French speakers at any level to comprehend and elaborate on.'||chr(10)||'With Coffee Hours, participants can work on their French speaking skills outside of the classroom, while also learning more about French culture and meeting new people. We also provide French snacks, such as crepes and croissants, for participants get a taste of French cuisine that they might not get otherwise.',null),
(168720,'Take Two: Seeking a Friend for the End of the World',cast('2012-09-08 19:00' as date),cast('2012-09-08 20:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','As an asteroid nears Earth, a man finds himself alone after his wife leaves in a panic. He decides to take a road trip to reunite with his high school sweetheart. Accompanying him is a neighbor who inadvertently puts a wrench in his plan.'||chr(10)||'Steve Carrell, Keira Knightly, and Melanie Lynskey; R; 101 min.; 2012.',null),
(194091,'Take Two: Brave',cast('2012-10-26 22:00' as date),cast('2012-10-26 22:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','Determined to make her own path in life, Princess Merida defies a custom that brings chaos to her kingdom. Granted one wish, Merida must rely on her bravery and her archery skills to undo a beastly curse.'||chr(10)||'Kelly Macdonald, Billy Connolly and Emma Thompson; Rated PG; 100 min.; 2012.',null),
(220056,'CAB Take Two: The Other Son',cast('2013-02-01 19:00' as date),cast('2013-02-01 21:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two presents The Other Son:'||chr(10)||'Two young men, one Israeli and one Palestinian, discover they were accidentally switched at birth.'||chr(10)||'from imdb.com',null),
(225019,'CAB Take Two: Anna Karenina',cast('2013-02-09 19:00' as date),cast('2013-02-09 21:15' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB TAKE TWO presents Anna Karenina:'||chr(10)||'Set in late-19th-century Russia high-society, the aristocrat Anna Karenina enters into a life-changing affair with the affluent Count Vronsky.',null),
(225021,'CAB Take Two: Here Comes the Boom',cast('2013-02-08 19:00' as date),cast('2013-02-08 21:15' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB TAKE TWO presents Here comes the Boom:'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'A high school biology teacher looks to become a successful mixed-martial arts fighter in an effort to raise money to prevent extra-curricular activities from being axed at his cash-strapped school.',null),
(281689,'CAB Take Two: Silver Linings Playbook',cast('2013-04-27 22:00' as date),cast('2013-04-27 22:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two present:'||chr(10)||'Silver Linings Playbook (Fri 7pm, Sat 3:30pm and 10pm) '||chr(10)||'After a stint in a mental institution, former teacher Pat Solitano moves back in with his parents and tries to reconcile with his ex-wife. Things get more challenging when Pat meets Tiffany, a mysterious girl with problems of her own.'||chr(10)||'The Hobbit: An Expected Journey (Fri 10pm, Sat 7pm) '||chr(10)||'A younger and more reluctant Hobbit, Bilbo Baggins, sets out on an "unexpected journey" to the Lonely Mountain with a spirited group of Dwarves to reclaim their stolen mountain home from a dragon named Smaug.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
