(1241487,'HSA Brown Bag Series Spring 2017',cast('2017-02-10 12:00' as date),cast('2017-02-10 13:00' as date),'Chapel Basement','Spirituality',NULL,'HINDU','The Hindu Students'' Association regroups students who identify culturally and spiritually as Hindus. The HSA has been organizing Brown Bags involving Professors and student members around different themes such as Hindus and the Indian Diaspora. This year we are planning to continuing this trend.',null),
