(777545,'Brothers Welcome Back BBQ',cast('2015-08-28 11:00' as date),cast('2015-08-28 12:00' as date),'Hudson Chapel','Social',NULL,'BROS','Brothers will hold it''s annual Welcome Back BBQ on the Quad outside of the Chapel',null),
(7939030,'Red Cross Blood Drive',cast('2022-02-03 12:00' as date),cast('2022-02-03 18:00' as date),'Hall of Presidents','Fundraising','Philanthropy','PDT','Red Cross will be coming to the Hall of Presidents on February 3, 2022 to collect blood donations. Anyone is welcome to donate.',null),
(798448,'Torchlight Brown Bag',cast('2015-11-12 12:00' as date),cast('2015-11-12 13:30' as date),'ALANA Multipurpose Room','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'THS','The Konosioni Senior Honor Society is proud to host the Torchlight Brown Bag. This event will begin with the history of the Torchlight Ceremony at Hudson: when and why it began. From there, concerns, thoughts, and feelings over the ceremony will be acknowledged and open for discussion. We hope to generate dialogue on what this tradition means to the Hudson community today. Join us to add to the conversation! ',null),
(8603063,'Kathak Dance Workshop',cast('2022-11-18 11:30' as date),cast('2022-11-18 16:00' as date),'301 Huntington Gymnasium (Session 1) or Chapel (Session 2)','Arts','Concert/Music','HINDU','Kathak is a versatile Indian classical dance form with challenging footwork, expressive facial expressions, and graceful hand movements. As kathaka means storyteller, performers convey stories through dance and offer entertainment in both religious and non-religious settings. In an interactive workshop, kathak artist and guru Pallavi Degwekar will discuss the history of kathak, introspection via music, math through rhythm, as well as teach beginner-level movements and spin techniques. '||chr(10)||'Please join us in celebrating this art form. Snacks will be catered by Royal Indian Grill. All are welcome and please register! Session 1 is 11:30-1:00 at 301 Huntington. Session 2 is 2:30-4:00 at Chapel.',null),
(8840569,'Spring 2023 Public Health Seminar: Patients, Providers, and the Experience of Care in the United States',cast('2023-02-02 12:00' as date),cast('2023-02-02 13:00' as date),'Batza Room','Thoughtful Learning',NULL,'HGHC','Please join us on Tuesday, February 7, from 5-7 pm in the Batza Room, for the Global Health Coalition''s Spring 2023 Public Health Seminar Health Inequality: Patients, Providers, and the Experience of Care in the United States by Professor Rebecca Upton. This event is co-sponsored by the Global Public and Environmental Health Program and the Hudson Pre-Health Pathways. ',null),
(9041575,'13 Days of Green - ALANA Spring Cleaning Swap',cast('2023-04-11 16:30' as date),cast('2023-04-11 19:30' as date),'ALANA Multipurpose Room','Community Service','Sustainability','COVE','Join us for the Spring Cleaning Swap hosted by ALANA and the Office of Sustainability.'||chr(10)||'Everyone is welcome to bring usable household goods, books, and clothes to ALANA during the donation drop-off time, and then come back to shop FOR FREE that evening!'||chr(10)||'By circulating reusable items, we can decrease our landfill waste at move-out, support fellow students needing items, and build connections within our community.'||chr(10)||'Donation Drop-off: 4:30 p.m. to 6:30 p.m.'||chr(10)||'Free Sale: 7 p.m. to 8:30 p.m.'||chr(10)||'Items accepted must be small enough to be carried by one person. Examples include:'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'Household items, such as hangers, plants, table fans, extension cords, etc.'||chr(10)||'Kitchen goods, such as pans, silverware, small appliances, etc.'||chr(10)||'Room decor, such as posters, tapestries, string lights, etc.'||chr(10)||'Clothing, including shoes and accessories'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'This event is part of the Office of Sustainabilitys 13 Days of Green series leading up to Earth Day.',null),
(909288,'Real Talk with Diane Ciccone',cast('2016-03-10 18:00' as date),cast('2016-03-10 19:30' as date),'Love Auditorium','Cultural',NULL,'SRT','Every year SORT hosts a series of events called Africana Womens Week in celebration of women of color, their diverse narratives, and their accomplishments. This years Africana Womens Week Keynote speaker is Diane Ciccone. Diane was not only a part of the first class of women to graduate from Hudson, but also one of the few black women.  Diane Ciccone has been an advocate for students of color and a support system for women of  color on Hudsons campus.  SORT invites all of Hudson campus to hear Dianes Story.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(9511261,'Farm To Table Dinner',cast('2023-10-16 16:30' as date),cast('2023-10-16 17:30' as date),'Chapel House','Social','Sustainability','CH','Attention all chefs, gardeners, or foodies: Come get cozy at Chapel House, learn how to make a beautiful soup, and delight in the fruits of your labor! Ingredients used will come from Hudson''s own organic garden. Email Kathy (kkeyes@hudson.edu) if youd like to come. Space is limited.',null),
(9824414,'Cupid''s Fever: Sex Toys Bingo',cast('2024-02-14 18:30' as date),cast('2024-02-14 20:30' as date),'COOP','Social',NULL,'ALANA','Welcome to another Sex Toys Bingo!'||chr(10)||'We would like to invite you to our annual Cupid''s Fever to celebrate Valentine''s Day. A lot of prizes (sex toys) await you along with the great information about healthy relationships, sexual pleasure, intimate hygiene, various body practices, and more!'||chr(10)||'Desserts, pastries, chocolate-covered strawberries and other aphrodisiacs will be served. '||chr(10)||'Grab a friend, partner, date, peer and come to enjoy cupid''s festivities and 15 rounds of bingo.'||chr(10)||'This event is being held in partnership with Shaw Wellness Institute, ALANA Cultural Center, First @ Hudson, Health and Wellness, Haven, Office of Equity and Diversity. ',null),
(8992318,'Pride Walk',cast('2023-03-29 18:30' as date),cast('2023-03-29 18:30' as date),'Center for Women''s Studies','Social',NULL,'HRPB','Join us for our 2023 Pride Walk led by our own Pep Band as we celebrate Queer Fest Week. '||chr(10)||'This year Queer Fest''s theme (as well as of the Lavender Graduation) is "With Pride We Thrive." This is a reminder to all of us that every single voice matters and that every single step we take in supporting each other fills the gap in the bridge of allyship. Following the maroon brick road, we must proceed with courage, patience, and pride - finding a place in our hearts for everyone. Pride is not only a feeling of being comfortable with who we are, but this is also a practice of sharing the confidence with others in need. By embracing this understanding of Pride, we will keep thriving for the decades to come.'||chr(10)||'The walk will begin at the Center for Women''s Studies and end at the Rainbow Room.',null),
(735198,'French Club Coffee Hour and Film Screenings',cast('2015-09-23 16:15' as date),cast('2015-09-23 16:00' as date),'Lawrence Hall 2nd floor','Cultural',NULL,'FC','Come enjoy a presentation on a Francophone topic with snacks included such as croissants every month with a Francophone film screening to follow that weekend.',null),
(200467,'Take Two: Dark Shadows',cast('2012-11-09 19:00' as date),cast('2012-11-09 21:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','An imprisoned vampire, Barnabas Collins, is set free and returns to his ancestral home, where his dysfunctional descendants are in need of his protection.'||chr(10)||'Johnny Depp, Michelle Pfeiffer and Eva Green; PG-13; 113 min.',null),
(206943,'Take Two: Expendables 2',cast('2012-11-30 19:00' as date),cast('2012-11-30 21:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','Last set of Take Two Movies for the semester!'||chr(10)||'Mr. Church reunites the Expendables for what should be an easy paycheck, but when one of their men is murdered on the job, their quest for revenge puts them deep in enemy territory and up against an unexpected threat.'||chr(10)||'Sylvester Stallone, Liam Hemsworth and Randy Couture; 2012; Rated R; 103 min.'||chr(10)||'-from imdb.com',null),
(233079,'CAB Take Two: Skyfall',cast('2013-03-02 22:00' as date),cast('2013-03-02 23:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two presents Skyfall:'||chr(10)||'Bond''s loyalty to M is tested when her past comes back to haunt her. Whilst MI6 comes under attack, 007 must track down and destroy the threat, no matter how personal the cost.'||chr(10)||'from imdb.com',null),
(249616,'CAB Take Two: Argo',cast('2013-04-05 22:00' as date),cast('2013-04-05 22:15' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents Oscar Winning Movies:'||chr(10)||'Django Unchained at 7:00PM and Argo at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, April 5th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, April 6th.'||chr(10)||'Django Unchained:'||chr(10)||'With the help of a German bounty hunter, a freed slave sets out to rescue his wife from a brutal Mississippi plantation owner.'||chr(10)||'Argo:'||chr(10)||'A dramatization of the 1980 joint CIA-Canadian secret operation to extract six fugitive American diplomatic personnel out of revolutionary Iran.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(285844,'CAB Take Two: Now You See Me',cast('2013-09-07 19:00' as date),cast('2013-09-07 20:45' as date),'Love Auditorium (Olin 300)',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents: The Great Gatsby at 7:00PM and Now You See Me at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Sept 6th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, Sept 7th.'||chr(10)||'The Great Gatsby (Fri:7pm, Sat:10pm): A Midwestern war veteran finds himself drawn to the past and lifestyle of his millionaire neighbor.'||chr(10)||'Now You See Me (Fri:10 pm, Sat:pm): An FBI agent and an Interpol detective track a team of illusionists who pull off bank heists during their performances and reward their audiences with the money.    ',null),
(289240,'CAB Take Two: This is the End',cast('2013-09-21 19:00' as date),cast('2013-09-21 20:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents: The Lone Ranger at 7:00PM and This is the End at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Sept 20th, and again at opposite times in on Saturday, Sept 21st.'||chr(10)||'The Lone Ranger (Fri 7pm and Sat 10pm)'||chr(10)||'Native American warrior Tonto recounts the untold tales that transformed John Reid, a man of the law, into a legend of justice. (starring Johnny Depp, Armie Hammer, William Fichtner)'||chr(10)||'This is the End (Fri 10pm and Sat 7pm)'||chr(10)||'While attending a party at James Franco''s house, Seth Rogen, Jay Baruchel and many other celebrities are faced with the apocalypse. (starring James Franco, Jonah Hill, Seth Rogen)'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'from imdb.com'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(314902,'CAB Take Two: Pacific Rim',cast('2013-10-19 22:00' as date),cast('2013-10-19 22:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents: Pacific Rim at 7:00PM and White House Down at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Oct 18th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, Oct 19th.'||chr(10)||'Pacific Rim (Fri 7pm/Sat 10pm)'||chr(10)||'As a war between humankind and monstrous sea creatures wages on, a former pilot and a trainee are paired up to drive a seemingly obsolete special weapon in a desperate effort to save the world from the apocalypse.'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'White House Down (Fri 10pm/Sat 7pm)'||chr(10)||'While on a tour of the White House with his young daughter, a Capitol policeman springs into action to save his child and protect the president from a heavily armed group of paramilitary invaders.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(314903,'CAB Take Two: White House Down',cast('2013-10-18 22:00' as date),cast('2013-10-18 22:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents: Pacific Rim at 7:00PM and White House Down at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Oct 18th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, Oct 19th.'||chr(10)||'Pacific Rim (Fri 7pm/Sat 10pm)'||chr(10)||'As a war between humankind and monstrous sea creatures wages on, a former pilot and a trainee are paired up to drive a seemingly obsolete special weapon in a desperate effort to save the world from the apocalypse.'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'White House Down (Fri 10pm/Sat 7pm)'||chr(10)||'While on a tour of the White House with his young daughter, a Capitol policeman springs into action to save his child and protect the president from a heavily armed group of paramilitary invaders.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(338852,'CAB Take Two: One Direction: This is Us',cast('2013-12-06 22:00' as date),cast('2013-12-06 23:45' as date),'love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents: The Mortal Instruments: City of Bones at 7:00PM and One Direction: This is Us at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Dec 6th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, Dec 7th.'||chr(10)||'The Mortal Instruments: City of Bones (Fri 7pm and Sat 10pm)'||chr(10)||'When her mother disappears, Clary Fray learns that she descends from a line of warriors who protect our world from demons. She joins forces with others like her and heads into a dangerous alternate New York called Downworld.'||chr(10)||'One Direction: This is Us (Fri 10pm and Sat 7pm)'||chr(10)||'A look at Niall, Zayn, Liam, Louis, and Harry''s meteoric rise to fame, from their humble hometown beginnings and competing on the X-Factor, to conquering the world and performing at London''s famed O2 Arena.',null),
(338856,'CAB Take Two: The Mortal Instruments',cast('2013-12-06 19:00' as date),cast('2013-12-06 21:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents: The Mortal Instruments: City of Bones at 7:00PM and One Direction: This is Us at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Dec 6th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, Dec 7th.'||chr(10)||'The Mortal Instruments: City of Bones (Fri 7pm and Sat 10pm)'||chr(10)||'When her mother disappears, Clary Fray learns that she descends from a line of warriors who protect our world from demons. She joins forces with others like her and heads into a dangerous alternate New York called Downworld.'||chr(10)||'One Direction: This is Us (Fri 10pm and Sat 7pm)'||chr(10)||'A look at Niall, Zayn, Liam, Louis, and Harry''s meteoric rise to fame, from their humble hometown beginnings and competing on the X-Factor, to conquering the world and performing at London''s famed O2 Arena.',null),
(345592,'The 13th Annual Green Summit',cast('2014-02-06 17:30' as date),cast('2014-02-06 19:30' as date),'Ho Atrium',NULL,'Sustainability','GEG','The Green Summit aims to gather Hudson students, professors, faculty, and Hamilton Community members for a two hour long event that will function as a think tank for environmental action in the Hudson area. There will be approximately eight groups that will have a green project that they hope to get accomplished by the end of the year. We will have existing green groups present in addition to new initiatives. All groups will utilize the Green Summit event as a way to propel their group with a clearly outlined plan of action. With a diverse population participating, we will increase the momentum of the established groups, while also jump-starting some new ones at the same time. This event will be held in the Ho Atrium on February 6th 2014 at 6PM. '||chr(10)||'We hope that every group will create a substantial action plan that will ultimately end up with its completion end of the semester/early spring semester in time for the annual green awards in which these groups will be recognized. We also hope that our new initiatives will be successful and follow through into whatever capacity they feel important.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(346159,'"Trashed" presented by Students for Environmental Action',cast('2014-02-19 19:00' as date),cast('2014-02-19 21:00' as date),'Ho 101',NULL,'Movie/Film','SEA','The 2012 documentary "Trashed" looks at the impacts of air, land, and water pollution at the global scale, specifically pollution caused by human overconsumption and waste.  The Students for Environmental Action spring film series will be continued with "Plasticized", a film about plastic pollution in the South Atlantic, next week.',null),
(365703,'CAB Take Two: The Best Man Holiday',cast('2014-01-31 20:00' as date),cast('2014-01-31 22:00' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Presents:'||chr(10)||'The Best Man Holiday at 8:00 PM and The Fifth Estate at 10:00 PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Jan 31th.'||chr(10)||'On Saturday Feb 1st: The Fifth Estate at 7:00PM and The Best Man Holiday at 10:00 PM'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'The Best Man Holiday (Fri 8:00PM and Sat 10:00PM)'||chr(10)||'When college friends reunite after 15 years over the Christmas holidays, they discover just how easy it is for long-forgotten rivalries and romances to be reignited. '||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'The Fifth Estate (Fri 10:00 PM and sat 7:00PM)'||chr(10)||'A dramatic thriller based on real events that reveals the quest to expose the deceptions and corruptions of power that turned an Internet upstart into the 21st century''s most fiercely debated organization.',null),
(403607,'CAB Take Two Midnight Movie: Captain America 2',cast('2014-04-05 00:00' as date),cast('2014-04-05 01:00' as date),'Hamilton Theater',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two presents Midnight Movie: Captain America: The Winter Soldier on April 5th, 12:00AM (Friday night) in Hamilton Theater'||chr(10)||'Captain America: The Winter Soldier (2014)'||chr(10)||'Starring Chris Evans, Samuel J. Jackson, Scarlett Johansson, and Sebastian Stan'||chr(10)||'Steve Rogers struggles to embrace his role in the modern world and battles a new threat from old history: the Soviet agent known as the Winter Soldier.'||chr(10)||'Free admission, pizza, and pop-corn with HUES Card.'||chr(10)||'Ware your super-hero outfit and win a prize!'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(403610,'CAB Take Two: About Time',cast('2014-03-29 22:00' as date),cast('2014-03-29 22:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Presents:'||chr(10)||'About Time at 7:00PM and Her at 10:00 PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Mar 28th.'||chr(10)||'On Saturday Mar 29th: Her at 7:00PM and About Time at 10:00 PM'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'About Time (Fri 7:00PM and Sat 10:00PM)'||chr(10)||'Starring  Domhnall Gleeson, Rachel McAdams, Bill Nighy'||chr(10)||'At the age of 21, Tim discovers he can travel in time and change what happens and has happened in his own life. His decision to make his world a better place by getting a girlfriend turns out not to be as easy as you might think.'||chr(10)||'Her (Fri 10:00 PM and sat 7:00PM)'||chr(10)||'Starring Joaquin Phoenix, Amy Adams, Scarlett Johansson '||chr(10)||'A lonely writer develops an unlikely relationship with his newly purchased operating system that''s designed to meet his every need.',null),
