(196141,'"Lost in Paradise" Movie Screening',cast('2012-11-15 19:00' as date),cast('2012-11-15 22:00' as date),'ALANA Multipurpose Room',NULL,'Movie/Film','HVS','Responding to the recent incident on campus during National Coming Out Week, Hudson Vietnam Society would like to present "Lost in Paradise," a "first Vietnamese gay film" and the winner of 2010 Technicolor Award (AFP). The story breaks new ground in its Vietnamese setting and the subject of homosexual relationship. Through this event, HVS would like to contribute in a meaningful way to the conversation on campus. It is also a way for non-Vietnamese Hudson students to learn about the emergence of the LGBTQ community in Vietnam in the last few years.',null),
