(281690,'CAB Take Two: The Hobbit',cast('2013-04-27 19:00' as date),cast('2013-04-27 20:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two present:'||chr(10)||'Silver Linings Playbook (Fri 7pm, Sat 3:30pm and 10pm) '||chr(10)||'After a stint in a mental institution, former teacher Pat Solitano moves back in with his parents and tries to reconcile with his ex-wife. Things get more challenging when Pat meets Tiffany, a mysterious girl with problems of her own.'||chr(10)||'The Hobbit: An Expected Journey (Fri 10pm, Sat 7pm) '||chr(10)||'A younger and more reluctant Hobbit, Bilbo Baggins, sets out on an "unexpected journey" to the Lonely Mountain with a spirited group of Dwarves to reclaim their stolen mountain home from a dragon named Smaug.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
