(527594,'HSA Brown Bag',cast('2014-12-05 12:15' as date),cast('2014-12-05 13:30' as date),'Hudson Chapel Basement','Spirituality','Religious/Spiritual','HINDU','Join us for our HSA Brown Bag Lunch!  '||chr(10)||'Our topic for this week will be: "Hindu fundamentalism, caste and race." We will explore the rise of the politics of "Hindutva" in recent years, the relationship between caste hierarchies in India, and racism, by way of Arundhati Roy''s recent critiques of Gandhi.',null),
