(333915,'CAB Take Two Classic Movies Weekend: Rocky',cast('2013-11-09 22:00' as date),cast('2013-11-09 23:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents CLASSIC MOVIES WEEKEND: Rocky at 7:00PM and Shawshank Redemption at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Nov 8th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, Nov 9th.'||chr(10)||'Rocky (Fri 7pm and Sat 10pm)'||chr(10)||'A small-time boxer gets a supremely rare chance to fight the heavy-weight champion in about in which he strives to go the distance for his self-respect.'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'Shawshank Redemption (Fri 10pm and Sat 7pm)'||chr(10)||'Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.',null),
