(2761042,'Hudson Actuarial Society Introductory Meeting',cast('2018-09-12 17:30' as date),cast('2018-09-12 17:30' as date),'Alumni 107','Group Business',NULL,'HDC','Get to know about the fields of Actuarial and Data Science. Learn what you could do now at Hudson to be at the top of the curve. ',null),
