(302815,'Take Two Saturday Matinee: Gravity',cast('2013-10-05 16:30' as date),cast('2013-10-05 17:00' as date),'Hamilton Movie Theater',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','NEW THIS YEAR:'||chr(10)||'CAB Take Two presents Satuday Matinee at the Hamilton Movie Theater. The new movie that''s in theater right now (Gravity) will be shown for FREE at 4:30pm this Saturday (October 5th).'||chr(10)||'The priority will go to Hudson students with their HUES Cards, then it''ll be open to everybody (maximum: 240).'||chr(10)||'Gravity (starring Sandra Bullock, George Clooney, Ed Harris)'||chr(10)||'A medical engineer and an astronaut work together to survive after an accident leaves them adrift in space.',null),
(333919,'CAB Take Two Classic Movies Weekend: The Shawshank Redemption',cast('2013-11-09 19:00' as date),cast('2013-11-09 21:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents CLASSIC MOVIES WEEKEND: Rocky at 7:00PM and Shawshank Redemption at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Nov 8th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, Nov 9th.'||chr(10)||'Rocky (Fri 7pm and Sat 10pm)'||chr(10)||'A small-time boxer gets a supremely rare chance to fight the heavy-weight champion in about in which he strives to go the distance for his self-respect.'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'The Shawshank Redemption (Fri 10pm and Sat 7pm)'||chr(10)||'Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.',null),
(338849,'CAB Take Two: One Direction: This is Us',cast('2013-12-07 19:00' as date),cast('2013-12-07 21:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents: The Mortal Instruments: City of Bones at 7:00PM and One Direction: This is Us at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Dec 6th, and again at opposite times on Saturday, Dec 7th.'||chr(10)||'The Mortal Instruments: City of Bones (Fri 7pm and Sat 10pm)'||chr(10)||'When her mother disappears, Clary Fray learns that she descends from a line of warriors who protect our world from demons. She joins forces with others like her and heads into a dangerous alternate New York called Downworld.'||chr(10)||'One Direction: This is Us (Fri 10pm and Sat 7pm)'||chr(10)||'A look at Niall, Zayn, Liam, Louis, and Harry''s meteoric rise to fame, from their humble hometown beginnings and competing on the X-Factor, to conquering the world and performing at London''s famed O2 Arena.',null),
(365706,'CAB Take Two: The Fifth Estate',cast('2014-02-01 19:00' as date),cast('2014-02-01 21:30' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Presents:'||chr(10)||'The Best Man Holiday at 8:00 PM and The Fifth Estate at 10:00 PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, Jan 31th.'||chr(10)||'On Saturday Feb 1st: The Fifth Estate at 7:00PM and The Best Man Holiday at 10:00 PM'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'The Best Man Holiday (Fri 8:00PM and Sat 10:00PM)'||chr(10)||'When college friends reunite after 15 years over the Christmas holidays, they discover just how easy it is for long-forgotten rivalries and romances to be reignited.'||chr(10)||' '||chr(10)||'The Fifth Estate (Fri 10:00 PM and sat 7:00PM)'||chr(10)||'A dramatic thriller based on real events that reveals the quest to expose the deceptions and corruptions of power that turned an Internet upstart into the 21st century''s most fiercely debated organization.',null),
(378424,'CAB Take Two: Fight Club',cast('2014-03-01 22:00' as date),cast('2014-03-01 23:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two presents The Classics Week. Come and enjoy some of the best classic movies of all time. On Friday Feb 28th, Fight Club at 7pm and Mean Girls at 10pm, and Saturday, Mar 1st, again at the opposite time.'||chr(10)||'Fight Club Friday 7pm and Sat 10 PM'||chr(10)||'An insomniac office worker looking for a way to change his life crosses paths with a devil-may-care soap maker and they form an underground fight club that evolves into something much, much more...'||chr(10)||'Mean Girls Friday 10 PM and Sat 7 PM'||chr(10)||'Cady Heron is a hit with The Plastics, the A-list girl clique at her new school, until she makes the mistake of falling for Aaron Samuels, the ex-boyfriend of alpha Plastic Regina George.',null),
