(244422,'CAB Take Two: Zero Dark Thirty',cast('2013-03-22 19:00' as date),cast('2013-03-22 20:45' as date),'Love Auditorium',NULL,'Movie/Film','SAA','CAB Take Two Movies presents:'||chr(10)||'Zero Dark Thirty at 7:00PM and Lincoln at 10:00PM in Love Auditorium on Friday, March 22nd, and again at opposite times on Saturday, March 23rd.'||chr(10)||'Zero Dark Thirty:'||chr(10)||'A chronicle of the decade-long hunt for al-Qaeda terrorist leader Osama bin Laden after the September 2001 attacks, and his death at the hands of the Navy S.E.A.L. Team 6 in May 2011.'||chr(10)||'Lincoln:'||chr(10)||'As the Civil War continues to rage, America''s president struggles with continuing carnage on the battlefield and as he fights with many inside his own cabinet on the decision to emancipate the slaves.'||chr(10)||' ',null),
(244424,'Film Screening of Kaleb',cast('2013-03-21 19:00' as date),cast('2013-03-21 20:00' as date),'Golden Auditorium, Little Hall',NULL,'Movie/Film','CSA','The movie Kaleb was part of the Haitian Film Festival and has won several awards. The director being of Haitian descent wanted to make a movie of important aspects of the world we live in and the importance of family. In addition to the film screening the producer Kervan Bartholomew will be here for a discussion afterwards and Caribbean food will be catered!!!! Summary: Kaleb has been kicked out of his home in Long Island, N.Y. for almost a year. His familys tense demeanor is apparent as they try to ignore the fact that Kaleb is not there. One day Jacque, Kalebs father, sees Kaleb in a local newspaper accused of raping a young girl. The police search for Kaleb and his friends while the incident sparks friction within the family, demanding Jacque to respond to his wifes ultimatum: FIND KALEB or LOSE THE REST OF HIS FAMILY. To learn more: http://kalebthemovie.com/ Hosted by CSA',null),
