(742631,'Screening of Sundance Film Festival Hit: Me and Earl and the Dying Girl',cast('2015-09-25 19:00' as date),cast('2015-09-25 20:00' as date),'Love Auditorium','Social',NULL,'SAA','Come watch the Sundance Film Festival hit, Me and Earl and the Dying Girl this weekend! Showings for this film are Friday at 7, and Saturday at 10 in Love Auditorium! '||chr(10)||'Synonpsis: High schooler Greg, who spends most of his time making parodies of classic movies with his co-worker Earl, finds his outlook forever altered after befriending a classmate who has just been diagnosed with cancer.',null),
