(954489,'Newman Retreat',cast('2016-10-28 15:30' as date),cast('2016-10-30 12:00' as date),'Good News Center','Spirituality',NULL,'NC','The Newman Community provides this retreat as a way for Catholics and non-Catholics alike to grow in their awareness of the Catholic faith through a weekend of prayer and activities.',null),
